e-satellite-development%2Farticleshow%2F104327047.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Firan-and-russia-initiate-talks-on-collaborative-satellite-development%2Famp_articleshow%2F104327047.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Firan-and-russia-initiate-talks-on-collaborative-satellite-development%2Famp_articleshow%2F104327047.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20a%20Columbia%20University%20student%20and%20an%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20reservist.%20I%20immediately%20made%20plans%20to%20return%20to%20Israel%20following%20Hamas'%20attacks%20even%20before%20I%20got%20my%20official%20call-up.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shira%20Guez%20(right)%20is%20a%2024-year-old%20Columbia%20University%20student%20and%20reservist%20in%20the%20Israeli%20Defense%20Force.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6525d4b368f1d46f52adea9b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221499%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShira%20Guez%20(right)%20is%20a%2024-year-old%20Columbia%20University%20student%20and%20reservist%20in%20the%20Israeli%20Defense%20Force.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Shira%20Guez%2FAlexi%20J.%20Rosenfeld%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EShira%20Guez%2C%2024%2C%20an%20Israeli%20student%20at%20Columbia%20University%2C%20flew%20back%20to%20Israel%20on%20Monday%20night.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EGuez%20is%20a%20reservist%20in%20the%20Israeli%20Defense%20Forces%20and%20was%20preparing%20to%20return%20even%20before%20she%20was%20called%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EShe%20told%20Insider%20that%20she%20was%20horrified%20by%20images%20of%20children%20who%20were%20hurt%20in%20Hamas%20attacks.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Shira%20Guez%2C%20a%2024-year-old%20Israeli%20student%20at%20Columbia%20University%20who%20is%20also%20a%20reservist%20in%20the%20Israeli%20Defense%20Forces.%20She%20spoke%20to%20Insider%20from%20the%20airport%20on%20Monday%20about%20her%20decision%20to%20leave%20New%20York%20and%20go%20back%20to%20Israel%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-invasion-gaza-root-out-hamas-would-be-nasty-fight-2023-10%5C%22%3EHamas%20launched%20a%20wave%20of%20attacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20country%20over%20the%20weekend.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20at%20Columbia%20University%20for%20two%20years.%20I%20study%20computer%20science.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20also%20an%20Israeli%20Defense%20Forces%20reservist%20from%20Ashdod%2C%20Israel.%20It's%20a%20city%20in%20the%20South.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20woke%20up%20on%20Saturday%20morning%20to%20a%20call%20from%20a%20friend%20and%20she%20told%20me%20there%20is%20a%20war.%20It's%20a%20serious%20war%20and%20from%20my%20personal%20experience%2C%20I%20feel%20we%20have%20never%20had%20something%20like%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20like%20a%20movie.%20It%20takes%20me%20back%20to%20the%20Holocaust.%20One%20picture%20really%20touched%20me%20of%20a%20child%20who%20was%20kidnapped%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20war%20and%20conflict%20around%20the%20world.%20But%20no%20matter%20what%20you%20are%20fighting%20about%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20the%20history%20is%2C%20there%20is%20no%20cause%20to%20make%20kids%20and%20women%20suffer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%2C%20honestly%2C%20is%20what%20really%20affected%20me%20to%20go%20and%20fight%20in%20this%20war.%20There%20is%20no%20reason%20that%20civilians%20should%20not%20just%20be%20killed%20but%20suffer%20before.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20saw%20this%20image%20I%20said%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20I%20will%20do%20in%20Israel.%20I%20just%20will%20go%20and%20find%20out.%20Because%20I%20can't%20be%20in%20the%20States%20when%20this%20is%20a%20kid%20that%20could%20be%20my%20brother.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20was%20no%20question%20I%20would%20volunteer.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20saw%20all%20those%20videos%20of%20what's%20happening%2C%20I%20said%2C%20I%20am%20so%20privileged%20to%20be%20here%20in%20New%20York%20and%20study%20computer%20science.%20But%20I%20can't%20do%20that.%20It%20felt%20to%20me%20like%20it%20would%20not%20be%20aligning%20with%20real%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%20night%2C%20I%20sent%20a%20message%20to%20all%20my%20commanders%20and%20said%20I%20wanted%20to%20come%20back%2C%20even%20before%20I%20got%20my%20official%20call.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20two%20years%20I%20was%20an%20officer%20in%20the%20military%20system%20and%20I%20know%20that%20I%20can%20contribute.%20I%20decided%20I%20would%20go%20even%20before%20I%20got%20called.%20I%20planned%20all%20my%20flights%20before%20I%20got%20the%20official%20call.%C2%A0And%20then%20this%20morning%2C%20I%20got%20called%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20will%20not%20do%20the%20duty%20I%20got%20called%20back%20for.%20I%20will%20do%20a%20duty%20that%20I%20volunteered%20to%20do.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20will%20be%20at%20Pikud%20(home%20front%20military%20command)%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%20basically%20the%20largest%20unit%20the%20army%20has.%20Whenever%20there%20is%20a%20situation%2C%20we%20need%20to%20figure%20out%20who%20to%20call%2C%20whether%20it%20be%20medical%20people%20or%20fighters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20fear.%20I%20was%20eager%20to%20get%20back%20because%20I%20feel%20there%20is%20a%20need.%20My%20country%20needs%20me%20and%20I%20will%20do%20whatever%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20believe%20that%20when%20we%20stick%20to%20our%20values%2C%20we%20win%20and%20we%20win%20only%20because%20we%20really%20care%20about%20this.%20Every%20building%20that%20we%20bomb%20and%20every%20different%20action%20we%20do%2C%20it%20comes%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20thought%20about%20the%20right%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20don't%20know%20how%20long%20the%20war%20will%20last.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20told%20my%20university%20I%20believe%20I%20will%20be%20back%20when%20it%20ends.%20A%20friend%20and%20I%20estimated%20it%20could%20be%20six%20months.%20But%20of%20course%2C%20there%20is%20no%20guarantee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20always%20believed%20in%20peace.%20I%20came%20here%20to%20the%20United%20States%20because%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20an%20ambassador.%20I%20came%20with%20zero%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20that%20everyone%20can%20help.%20They%20just%20need%20to%20think%20about%20how.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20song%20in%20the%20back%20of%20my%20head%20that%20there%20is%20a%20hope%20of%20peace%20for%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-gaza-columbia-student-idf-reservist-going-back-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696979900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6525d6a855f52b01b35bd194%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-gaza-columbia-student-idf-reservist-going-back-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shira%20Guez%2C%20a%2024-year-old%20Columbia%20student%20and%20Israeli%20Defense%20Forces%20reservist%2C%20said%20images%20from%20this%20weekend's%20attacks%20remind%20her%20of%20the%20Holocaust.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22esnodgrass%40insider.com%20(Erin%20Snodgrass)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-gaza-columbia-student-idf-reservist-going-back-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Birkenstock%3A%20Once-uncool%20sandal%20maker%20now%20worth%20billions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696979746000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%