planning%20to%20execute.%20One%20such%20aspect%20of%20this%20effort%20is%20gathering%20intelligence%20before%20forces%20potentially%20move%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUndoubtedly%2C%20the%20Israeli%20defense%20military%20planners%20and%20decision-makers%20are%20trying%20to%20get%20as%20granular%20of%20a%20view%20as%20possible%2C%20particularly%20in%20an%20urban%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Borene%2C%20who%20served%20as%20a%20special%20security%20officer%20in%20the%20US%20Marine%20Corps%20during%20the%202003%20invasion%20of%20Iraq.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20collect%20as%20much%20information%20as%20possible%20on%20the%20battle%20space%20%E2%80%94%20from%20whatever%20sources%20necessary%20%E2%80%94%20and%20send%20it%20down%20to%20individual%20soldiers%20at%20the%20tactical%20level%20who%20may%20find%20themselves%20battling%20a%20force%20fighting%20irregularly%20within%20Gaza.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20major%20challenge%20for%20the%20Israelis%20in%20this%20space%2C%20Borene%20added%2C%20is%20that%20because%20Gaza%20is%20an%20urban%20environment%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20can%20be%20difficult%20to%20get%20imagery%20inside%20of%20buildings%2C%20in%20covered%20areas.%20But%20they're%20going%20to%20want%20to%20protect%20innocent%20civilian%20lives%20and%20protect%20the%20lives%20of%20their%20own%20troops.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20intelligence%20that%20Israel%20is%20able%20to%20collect%20before%20any%20invasion%20would%20come%20into%20play%20as%20ground%20troops%20moved%20in.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20after%20the%20potential%20assault%20begins%2C%20every%20individual%20soldier%20and%20vehicle%20becomes%20an%20intelligence%20sensor%20with%20the%20ability%20to%20communicate%20intelligence%20in%20both%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTaking%20that%20granular%20tactical%20operator%26quot%3B%20and%20making%20sure%20%26quot%3Btheir%20observations%20feed%20back%20into%20a%20collective%20picture%20accurately%20so%20that%20the%20maneuver%20commanders%20can%20do%20things%20like%20prevent%20unnecessary%20loss%20of%20civilian%20life%20and%20get%20a%20better%2C%20more%20accurate%20picture%20of%20where%20hazards%20may%20exist%20for%20sabotage%20or%20for%20ambush%26quot%3B%20is%20crucial%2C%20Borene%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smoke%20rises%20following%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike%20on%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20on%20October%2010%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6525c2f168f1d46f52add515%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESmoke%20rises%20following%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike%20on%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20on%20October%2010%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20Momen%20Faiz%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInside%20any%20potential%20battlespace%2C%20Israel%20has%20significantly%20more%20firepower%20than%20the%20Iran-backed%20Hamas%2C%C2%A0but%20the%20latter%20still%20poses%20a%20threat.%20It's%20unclear%20how%20much%20capability%20the%20militant%20group%20lost%20during%20its%20initial%20attacks%20%E2%80%94%20as%20many%20as%201%2C500%20Palestinian%20militants%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fliveblog_entry%2Fhamas-770-dead-in-gaza-4000-wounded%2F%5C%22%3Ereportedly%3C%2Fa%3E%20been%20killed%20by%20the%20IDF%20since%20Saturday%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20also%20unclear%20how%20many%20more%20may%20await%20Israeli%20forces%20in%20Gaza.%20The%20Times%20of%20Israel%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fsenior-idf-commander-says-hamas-has-7000-rockets-dozens-of-drones%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202021%20that%20Hamas%20may%20have%20up%20to%2030%2C000%20men%2C%20thousands%20of%20rockets%2C%20and%20hundreds%20of%20anti-tank%20and%20anti-aircraft%20missiles%20in%20its%20arsenal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20given%20the%20attack%20Hamas%20launched%20against%20Israel%2C%20it%20is%20likely%20anticipating%20retaliation%20and%20further%20fighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHamas%20has%20been%20preparing%20for%20attacking%20Israel%20and%20also%20defending%20Gaza%20for%20decades%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20Spencer%2C%20a%20former%20US%20Army%20infantry%20soldier%20who%20served%20two%20combat%20deployments%20to%20Iraq%2C%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BSo%20you%20can%20believe%20that%20they've%20stockpiled%20a%20lot%20of%20weapons%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20rockets%20for%20attacking%20into%20Israel%2C%20but%20for%20attacking%20a%20possible%20ground%20invasion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpencer%2C%20now%20the%20chair%20of%20urban%20warfare%20studies%20at%20West%20Point's%20Modern%20War%20Institute%2C%20said%20the%20ability%20of%20Hamas%20to%20launch%20rockets%20will%20be%20an%20important%20characteristic%20of%20this%20war%2C%20as%20it%20will%20likely%20continue%20to%20lob%20the%20munitions%20at%20Israeli%20cities%20and%20also%20toward%20the%20approaching%20IDF%20soldiers.%20Beyond%20the%20rockets%2C%20Hamas%20can%20also%20use%20drones%2C%20roadside%20bombs%2C%20and%20its%20elaborate%20network%20of%20tunnels%20%E2%80%94%20which%20the%20IDF%20previously%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.idf.il%2Fen%2Fmini-sites%2Fhamas%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-hamas-underground-city-of-terror%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edescribed%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bvast%20underground%20city%20with%20dozens%20of%20access%20points%20located%20throughout%20Gaza%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20to%20launch%20surprise%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20enter%20a%20contested%20urban%20area%2C%20you%20basically%20have%20to%20enter%20in%20with%20your%20face%20and%20wait%20until%20you%20get%20punched%20in%20the%20face%20before%20you%20know%20where%20to%20engage%2C%26quot%3B%20Spencer%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20enemy%20gets%20first%20shot%20in%20an%20urban%20defense.%20But%20usually%20that%20means%20...%20now%20the%20enemy%20has%20identified%20itself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3