Sam%20Bankman-Fried's%20risk%20appetite%20was%20so%20large%20that%20he%20would%20flip%20a%20coin%20if%20losing%20meant%20destroying%20the%20world%2C%20Caroline%20Ellison%20testified%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Caroline%20Ellison%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63a61cd646a5550018b7deda%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETyler%20Le%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESam%20Bankman-Fried%20said%20he%20was%20willing%20to%20destroy%20the%20world%20with%20a%20coin%20flip%2C%20Caroline%20Ellison%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20testified%20that%20SBF%20used%20the%20metaphor%20to%20illustrate%20his%20risk%20philosophy%20for%20Alameda%20investments.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20lost%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EImagine%2C%20if%20you%20will%2C%20a%20coin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20flip%20it%20and%20get%20heads%2C%20the%20entire%20world%20improves%20by%20more%20than%20double.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20get%20tails%2C%20the%20world%20is%20destroyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESam%20Bankman-Fried%20said%20he%20would%20flip%20the%20coin%20%E2%80%94%20and%20urged%20everyone%20else%20to%20do%20so%2C%20too%2C%20Caroline%20Ellison%20testified%20in%20court%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcaroline-ellison-testify-criminal-trial-ftx-collapse-sam-bankman-fried-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20witness%20stand%20at%20Bankman-Fried's%20criminal%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ellison%2C%20the%20former%20CEO%20of%20his%20cryptocurrency%20hedge%20fund%20Alameda%20Research%2C%20said%20Bankman-Fried%20often%20talked%20about%2050%25-chance-of-apocalypse%20coin%20flip%20to%20illustrate%20his%20investment%20philosophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried%20%26quot%3Bdescribed%20himself%20as%20truly%20risk-neutral%2C%26quot%3B%20Ellison%20said%2C%20meaning%20he%20was%20completely%20comfortable%20taking%20risks%20as%20long%20as%20the%20average%20expected%20value%20of%20the%20bet%20was%20positive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20also%20talked%20about%20this%20in%20the%20context%20of%20thinking%20about%20what%20was%20good%20for%20the%20world%2C%20saying%20that%20he%20would%20be%20happy%20to%20flip%20a%20coin%2C%26quot%3B%20Ellison%20testified%20Tuesday.%20%26quot%3BIf%20it%20came%20up%20tails%20and%20the%20world%20was%20destroyed%2C%20as%20long%20as%20it%20came%20up%20heads%20the%20world%20would%20be%20like%20more%20than%20twice%20as%20good.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried's%20love%20of%20shady%20coins%2C%20risky%20bets%2C%20and%20risky%20bets%20with%20shady%20coins%20have%20become%20central%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-sbf-fraud-trial-ftx-explainer-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehis%20criminal%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20he%20faces%20seven%20criminal%20counts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20allege%20Bankman-Fried%20defrauded%20customers%20and%20investors%20of%20FTX%2C%20his%20now-defunct%20cryptocurrency%20exchange%2C%20by%20siphoning%20their%20funds%20to%20Alameda%20Research%2C%20his%20cryptocurrency%20hedge%20fund%2C%20without%20their%20knowledge%20or%20permission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%20in%20the%20trial%2C%20prosecutors%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-trial-adam-yedidia-bug-8-billion-alameda-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Easked%20witnesses%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20Bankman-Fried's%20enormous%20appetite%20for%20risk%20and%20his%20high-wire%20act%20of%20borrowing%20enormous%20funds%20to%20make%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20customer%20funds%2C%20Ellison%20testified%20in%20federal%20court%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Alameda%20made%20its%20crypto%20bets%20using%20money%20from%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20loans%20%E2%80%94%20including%20from%20companies%20like%20the%20crypto%20trading%20firm%20Genesis%20%E2%80%94%20often%20had%20extremely%20risky%20terms%2C%20Ellison%20said.%20They%20allowed%20lenders%20to%20ask%20for%20their%20money%20back%20at%20any%20time%2C%20she%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried%20directed%20Ellison%20and%20other%20employees%20of%20Alameda%20Research%20to%20get%20as%20many%20enormous%20loans%20as%20possible%20anyway%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEllison%20testified%20about%20a%20point%20in%20time%20in%202021%20when%20Bankman-Fried%20wanted%20to%20spend%20%243%20billion%20on%20venture%20investments.%20Those%20investments%2C%20Ellison%20said%2C%20would%20be%20difficult%20to%20sell%2C%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20liquidity%20could%20cause%20a%20problem%20if%20lenders%20wanted%20their%20money%20back.%20In%20addition%2C%20she%20said%2C%20Alameda%20Research%20already%20had%20around%20%242.7%20billion%20in%20liabilities%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20assumed%20it%20would%20significantly%20increase%20the%20risk%20if%20we%20couldn't%20meet%20loan%20recalls%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried%20didn't%20seem%20too%20concerned%2C%20Ellison%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20assumed%20Alameda%20would%20use%20FTX%20customer%20funds%20to%20repay%20our%20loans%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20media%20interviews%2C%20Bankman-Fried%20has%20said%20that%2C%20following%20FTX's%20apparent%20collapse%20in%20November%20of%202022%2C%20he%20could%20have%20made%20everyone%20whole%20if%20only%20he%20had%20more%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20opening%20statement%20for%20the%20trial%2C%20his%20attorneys%20said%20Ellison%20%E2%80%94%20who%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20four%20criminal%20counts%20herself%20and%20is%20testifying%20as%20part%20of%20a%20cooperation%20agreement%20%E2%80%94%20should%20have%20heeded%20Bankman-Fried's%20instructions%20during%20the%20cryptocurrency%20downturn%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20spoke%20to%20Ms.%20Ellison%2C%20the%20CEO%2