%20criminal%20trial%20in%20a%20downtown%20Manhattan%20federal%20courtroom%20on%20Tuesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20our%20personal%20relationship%2C%20there%20was%20a%20feeling%20that%20I%20wanted%20more%20in%20our%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20Ellison%20testified.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20felt%20like%20he%20was%20distant%20or%20not%20paying%20enough%20attention%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEllison%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcaroline-ellison-testify-criminal-trial-ftx-collapse-sam-bankman-fried-2023-9%5C%22%3Espilled%20the%20tea%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20front%20of%20jurors%2C%20the%20judge%2C%20lawyers%2C%20and%20more%20than%20100%20journalists%20and%20onlookers%20in%20the%20courtroom%20and%20two%20overflow%20rooms%20in%20the%20Manhattan%20courthouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20two%20began%20a%20romantic%20relationship%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202019.%20They%20had%20met%20a%20few%20years%20prior%20when%20she%20was%20an%20intern%20at%20Jane%20Street%20and%20Bankman-Fried%20was%20a%20trader.%20Bankman-Fried%20convinced%20her%20to%20join%20his%20own%20hedge%20fund%2C%20Alameda%20Research%2C%20as%20a%20trader%20in%202017%20and%20she%20became%20co-CEO%20of%20the%20company%20in%202021%20and%20the%20sole%20CEO%20in%202022%2C%20ahead%20of%20its%20collapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20started%20sleeping%20together%20on%20and%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20Ellison%20said%2C%20telling%20the%20courtroom%20that%20the%20pair%20began%20formally%20dating%20in%202020.%20They%20tried%20to%20keep%20the%20relationship%20private%20from%20their%20coworkers%20at%20FTX%20and%20Alameda%2C%20but%20word%20got%20around%2C%20Ellison%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20time%20we%20were%20dating%2C%20he%20was%20also%20my%20boss%2C%20so%20that%20created%20some%20awkward%20situations%2C%26quot%3B%20Ellison%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pair%20were%20in%20an%20on-and-off%20relationship%20until%20the%20spring%20of%202022%2C%20when%20Ellison%20said