%20height%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESmoke%20rises%20after%20bombing%20of%20Israeli%20forces%20with%20warplanes%20in%20Gaza%20City%2C%20October%207%2C%202023.%20Another%20munition%20can%20be%20seen%20falling%20toward%20a%20target.%3Cp%3EMomen%20Faiz%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EIsrael's%20Air%20Force%20is%20conducting%20devastating%20airstrikes%20on%20Gaza.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EVideos%20appear%20to%20show%20strikes%20employing%20precision-guided%20munitions%20and%20missiles%20against%20Hamas%20targets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20strikes%20are%20destroying%20the%20area%20as%20violence%20only%20escalates%20after%20Hamas%20staged%20a%20brutal%20attack.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20airstrikes%20are%20pummeling%20Hamas%20militants%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20in%20moves%20that%20could%20be%20a%20precursor%20to%20expanded%20combat%20operations%2C%20and%20the%20country%20is%20requesting%20more%20weapons%20as%20the%20fighting%20continues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20airstrikes%20began%20early%20in%20the%20worsening%20conflict%20that%20started%20with%20a%20bloody%20surprise%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20on%20Saturday%20that%20killed%20at%20least%20800%20people%20%E2%80%94%20mostly%20civilians%20%E2%80%94%20and%20wounded%20countless%20more.%20Deaths%20have%20climbed%20since%20the%20initial%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20have%20said%20its%20strikes%20are%20targeting%20Hamas%20forces%20across%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20but%20the%20area%20is%20densely%20populated%20with%20around%202%20million%20people%2C%20many%20families%20with%20children.%20Combat%20in%20this%20area%20is%20a%20challenge%2C%20and%20Palestinian%20officials%20said%20at%20least%20830%20people%20have%20died%20since%20the%20airstrikes%20began.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FMirandaCleland%2Fstatus%2F1711829748286980384%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3EAt%20least%20260%