Fphoto%2F104324688.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAmitabh%20Bachchan%20greets%20his%20fans%20on%20his%20birthday%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20fans%20spot%20Aishwarya%20Rai%20Bachchan%20and%20Navya%20Nanda%20video-calling%20and%20taking%20videos%20of%20him...%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ffans-spot-aishwarya-rai-bachchan-aaradhya-and-navya-nanda-as-amitabh-bachchan-greets-fans-on-his-birthday-abhishek-bachchan-reacts-watch-video%2Farticleshow%2F104324688.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chief%20Justice's%20Concern%20For%20Unborn%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20To%20Review%20Abortion%20Order%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETrying%20to%20strike%20a%20balance%20between%20the%20life%20of%20an%20unborn%20child%20and%20the%20pleas%20of%20a%20mother%20who%20said%20she%20would%20be%20unable%20to%20raise%20it%2C%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20expressed%20concern%20and%20ordered%20a%20review%20of%20a%20judgment%20made%20by%20a%20two-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20same%20court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20a%20different%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20allowed%20the%20couple%20to%20abort%20their%2026-week-old%20pregnancy%20after%20the%20petitioner%20argued%20that%20the%20woman%2C%20who%20is%20a%20mother%20of%20two%20children%2C%20is%20suffering%20from%20various%20health%20issues%20and%20from%20postnatal%20depression.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Dilemma%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20medical%20board%20formed%20by%20AIIMS%20said%20the%20baby%20is%20currently%20viable%20(showing%20signs%20of%20life%20and%20having%20a%20strong%20possibility%20of%20survival)%20adding%20that%20they%20need%20a%20directive%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20whether%20a%20feticide(%20stopping%20the%20fetal%20heart)%20be%20performed%20before%20the%20termination%20of%20the%2026-week-old%20unwanted%20pregnancy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20said%20the%20procedure%20is%20performed%20in%20cases%20when%20the%20foetus%20has%20an%20abnormal%20development%2C%20but%20it%20is%20generally%20not%20performed%20on%20a%20normal%20foetus.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20AIIMS%20panel%20stressed%20that%20if%20a%20feticide%20is%20not%20performed%20then%20it%20will%20not%20be%20termed%20as%20termination%2C%20but%20a%20preterm%20delivery%20where%20the%20baby%20needs%20intensive%20treatment%20and%20care.%20A%20baby%20born%20preterm%20needs%20intensive%20care%20and%20there%20is%20a%20high%20possibility%20that%20it%20can%20cause%20physical%20and%20mental%20disability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditional%20Solicitor%20General%20(ASG)%20Aishwarya%20Bhati%20told%20the%20bench%20headed%20by%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20that%20the%20report%20from%20AIIMS%20is%20not%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20judgment%20that%20was%20given%20earlier.%20Ms%20Bhati%20said%20the%20foetus%20would%20be%20born%20alive%20and%20would%20be%20murder%20and%20not%20abortion%20of%20the%20baby.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20understood%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20situation%20and%20ordered%20that%20a%20bench%20be%20constituted%20tomorrow%20to%20hear%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Previous%20Judgment%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Hima%20Kohli%20and%20Justice%20BV%20Nagarathna%20said%20they%20respect%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20petitioner%20after%20the%20woman%20argued%20that%20she%20is%20a%20mother%20of%20two%20children%20and%20is%20suffering%20from%20various%20health-related%20issues.%20The%20woman%20said%20she%20is%20financially%2C%20emotionally%20and%20socially%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20raise%20a%20third%20child%20while%20she%20is%20already%20breastfeeding%20her%20second%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%2C%20in%20her%20petition%2C%20said%20the%20medical%20report%20mentioned%20that%20pregnancy%20does%20not%20occur%20during%20Lateral%20Amenorrhea%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20didn't%20know%20whether%20she%20could%20get%20pregnant%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20AIIMS%20panel%20said%20a%20directive%20needs%20to%20be%20given%20on%20whether%20the%20parents%20agree%20to%20raise%20the%20child%20considering%20that%20it%20could%20cause%20a%20major%20physical%2C%20emotional%20and%20financial%20toll%20on%20the%20couple.%20If%20the%20couple%20agrees%20to%20adoption%2C%20then%20a%20clear%20process%20should%20be%20laid%20out%20to%20ensure%20a%20better%20future%20for%20the%20baby.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Medical%20Termination%20of%20Pregnancy%20(MTP)%20Act%2C%20the%20upper%20limit%20for%20the%20termination%20of%20pregnancy%20is%2024%20weeks%20for%20married%20women%2C%20special%20categories%20including%20survivors%20of%20rape%20and%20other%20vulnerable%20women%20such%20as%20the%20differently-abled%20and%20minors.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696970340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fgv8pfg28_supreme-court_625x300_04_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-dy-chandrachuds-concern-for-unborn-supreme-court-to-review-abortion-order-4468835%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Just%2024%20hours%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ordered%20a%20medical%20termination%20of%20pregnancy%20of%20a%2026-week-old%20pregnant%20mother%2C%20the%20Centre%20cited%20a%20serious%20dilemma%20that%20the%20unborn%20child%20can%20be%20alive%20if%20aborted.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-dy-chandrachuds-concern-for-unborn-supreme-court-to-review-abortion-order-4468835%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-dy-chandrachuds-concern-for-unborn-supreme-court-to-review-abo