n%20Netanyahu%20has%20warned%20Israel's%20military%20campaign%20following%20Saturday's%20onslaught%20was%20only%20the%20start%20of%20a%20sustained%20war%20to%20destroy%20Hamas%20and%20%26quot%3Bchange%20the%20Middle%20East%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFears%20of%20a%20regional%20conflagration%20have%20surged%20amid%20expectations%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-ndtv-journalists-safe-after-rocket-hits-their-hotel-in-israel-4468617%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elooming%20Israeli%20ground%20incursion%20into%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20crowded%20enclave%20from%20where%20Hamas%20launched%20its%20land%2C%20air%2C%20and%20sea%20attack%20on%20the%20Jewish%20Sabbath.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20count%20in%20Israel%20has%20surged%20above%20900%20from%20the%20worst%20attack%20in%20the%20country's%2075-year%20history%2C%20while%20Gaza%20officials%20have%20reported%20765%20people%20killed%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplained-how-hamas-gets-weapons-in-gaza-and-the-taliban-connection-israel-gaza-war-gaza-airstrikes-gaza-4468096%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHamas%20gunmen%20killed%20more%20than%20100%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20kibbutz%20of%20Beeri%20alone%2C%20said%20Moti%20Bukjin%2C%20a%20volunteer%20with%20the%20charity%20Zaka%20that%20recovers%20bodies%20in%20accordance%20with%20Jewish%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20shot%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20AFP.%20%26quot%3BThey%20murdered%20in%20cold%20blood%20children%2C%20babies%2C%20old%20people%20--%20everyone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BHamas%20is%20ISIS%26quot%3B%3A%20Benjamin%C2%A0Netanyahu%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EPM%20Netanyahu%20compared%20the%20large-scale%20slaughter%20of%20Israeli%20civilians%20to%20the%20atrocities%20committed%20by%20the%20Islamic%20State%20group%2C%20also%20known%20as%20ISIS%2C%20when%20they%20contro