ate%20aspirations%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%26quot%3B%20but%20said%20Hamas%20%26quot%3Boffers%20nothing%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20other%20than%20more%20terror%20and%20bloodshed%26quot%3B%2C%20in%20a%20joint%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20five%20Western%20powers%20and%20many%20other%20nations%20have%20reported%20citizens%20killed%2C%20abducted%20or%20missing%2C%20also%20including%20Brazil%2C%20Cambodia%2C%20Canada%2C%20Ireland%2C%20Mexico%2C%20Nepal%2C%20Panama%2C%20Paraguay%2C%20Russia%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Thailand%20and%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fshould-do-anything-to-get-our-citizens-back-jerusalem-dy-mayor-to-ndtv-4468031%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHamas%20has%20held%20around%20150%20hostages%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20its%20ground%20incursion%2C%20among%20them%20children%2C%20elderly%20and%20young%20people%20who%20were%20captured%20at%20a%20music%20festival%20where%20some%20270%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Hamas%20warned%20it%20would%20start%20killing%20hostages%20every%20time%20Israel%20launches%20a%20strike%20on%20a%20civilian%20target%20in%20Gaza%20without%20warning.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFear%20reigns%20among%20Palestinians%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EFear%20and%20chaos%20reigned%20among%20the%202.3%20million%20Palestinians%20living%20in%20the%20crowded%20and%20impoverished%20coastal%20territory%20that%20has%20been%20hammered%20by%20thousands%20of%20Israeli%20bombs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFireballs%20repeatedly%20lit%20up%20Gaza%20City%20before%20dawn%20Tuesday%20as%20explosions%20shook%20the%20ground%20and%20sirens%20wailed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20distraught%20man%20was%20seen%20carrying%20the%20shrouded%20body%20of%20a%20child%20in%20Khan%20Yunis%2C%20in%20the%20south%20of%20the%20enclave%2C%20where%20other%20remains%20were%20piled%20onto%20the%20back%20of%20pickup%20trucks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20similar%20scenes%20in%20th