r%20and%20barricaded%20the%20affected%20areas%2C%20while%20some%20of%20the%20guests%20were%20seen%20moving%20out%2C%20filling%20bags%20with%20just%20essential%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bombing%20took%20place%20as%20the%20NDTV%20team%20was%20on%20their%20way%20to%20the%20hotel%20after%20Hamas%20threats%20that%20airstrikes%20will%20begin%20in%20Ashkelon.%20But%20there%20was%20little%20time%20for%20the%20residents%20to%20evacuate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20team%20landed%20in%20Ashkelon%20--%20a%20coastal%20city%20just%20a%20few%20kilometers%20from%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20--%20on%20Sunday%20night%2C%20there%20have%20been%20frequent%20air%20raid%20warnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20check-in%20at%20the%20hotel%20was%20interrupted%20by%20an%20air%20raid%20siren%2C%20during%20which%20the%20team%20had%20to%20abandon%20their%20luggage%20and%20sprint%20for%20shelter%20in%20the%20basement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20of%20the%20day%20was%20dotted%20with%20similar%20experiences.%20The%20Hamas%20rockets%2C%20though%2C%20were%20intercepted%20by%20the%20Israeli%20Iron%20Dome%2C%20a%20mobile%20all-weather%20air%20defense%20system%20that%20tracks%20and%20intercepts%20missile.%3Cbr%3E%20But%20given%20the%20barrage%20of%20rockets%20from%20the%20other%20side%2C%20once%20in%20a%20while%20a%20rocket%20managed%20to%20slip%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELocated%20on%20the%20Mediterranean%20coast%2C%20Ashkelon%2C%20known%20for%20its%20archaeological%20site%20and%20the%20world's%20largest%20seawater%20reverse%20osmosis%20desalination%20plant%2C%20appears%20deserted%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20bore%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%20attack%20on%20Saturday%20--%20when%20Hamas%20launched%20an%20air%2C%20sea%20and%20ground%20attack%20--%20with%20many%20homes%20lasted%20by%20Hamas%20rockets.%20The%20hospitals%20have%20their%20hands%20full%20treating%20the%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20Israel%20retaliated%20with%20a%20declaration%20of%20war.%20More%20than%201%