www.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-us-canada-67070505%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delimitation%20Should%20Not%20Solely%20Be%20Determined%20by%20Numerical%20Superiority%3A%20Former%20SC%20Judge%20Chelameswar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F10192713%2FScreenshot-2023-10-10-at-7.26.25%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ERetired%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20Justice%20Jasti%20Chelameswar%20asked%20whether%20there%20should%20be%20a%20pattern%20where%20somebody%20gets%20a%20premium%20for%20their%20nonperformance%2C%20with%20the%20South%20Indian%20states%20paying%20for%20the%20nonperforming%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20speaking%20during%20a%20panel%20discussion%20on%20%E2%80%9CDelimitation%3A%20Southern%20Discomfort%20And%20Solutions%E2%80%9D%20at%20Dakshin%20Dialogues%202023%2C%20the%20annual%20flagship%20thought%20conclave%20of%C2%A0%3Cem%3ESouth%20First%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20Saturday%2C%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20matter%20of%20delimitation%20and%20%E2%80%98One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Vote%E2%80%99%20should%20be%20debated%20seriously.%20Funds%20from%20the%20government%20of%20India%20are%20being%20used%20for%20the%20different%20states%E2%80%A6%20Some%20of%20us%20in%20some%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20are%20not%20being%20cared%20for%20so%20well.%20Something%20is%20required%20to%20be%20done.%20But%20should%20it%20be%20such%20a%20pattern%20that%20somebody%20gets%20a%20premium%20for%20their%20non-performance%3F%20How%20to%20solve%20it%3F%20That%E2%80%99s%20a%20matter%20which%20should%20be%20discussed%20along%20the%20line%20of%20delimitation%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Justice%20Chelameswar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20amending%20the%20constitution%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20was%20a%20legal%20document%20that%20deserved%20the%20utmost%20respect%3A%20It%20was%20crucial%20not%20to%20view%20it%20as%20something%20infallible%2C%20but%20rather%20subject%20to%20scrutiny%20and%20adaptation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20aspect%20has%20been%20a%20topic%20of%20discussion%20for%20the%20past%2075%20years%2C%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%20when%20questions%20arose%20about%20whether%20the%20constitution%20could%20be%20amended%20by%20parliament%2C%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20in%201973%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20that%20the%20constitution%20could%20be%20amended%20by%20parliament%2C%20with%20the%20limitation%20that%20the%20basic%20structure%20of%20the%20constitution%20could%20not%20be%20altered.%20Defining%20what%20constitutes%20this%20%E2%80%98basic%20structure%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20complex%20task%2C%20akin%20to%20traditional%20Indian%20philosophy%20%E2%80%93%20it%E2%80%99s%20challenging%20to%20explain%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20was%20also%20worth%20noting%20that%20there%20were%20aspects%20of%20the%20constitution%20that%20might%20benefit%20from%20periodic%20reevaluation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20may%20have%20been%20suitable%20a%20century%20ago%20may%20require%20reexamination%20through%20rigorous%20and%20intelligent%20debate%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explained.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20process%20should%20not%20be%20solely%20determined%20by%20shouting%20and%20numerical%20superiority%3B%20it%20demands%20thoughtful%20consideration.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FWm4g7lQi1zA%3Fsi%3Db1ZfH2T7bbEVDEMK%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20interpreting%20the%20constitution%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20framers%20of%20the%20constitution%20were%20individuals%20of%20great%20wisdom%2C%20with%20vast%20experience%20and%20deep%20commitment%20to%20the%20nation%2C%20noted%20the%20retired%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%2C%20adding%20that%20many%20of%20them%20endured%20prolonged%20periods%20of%20incarceration%20during%20the%20British%20colonial%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETheir%20sacrifices%20and%20dedication%20to%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20development%20and%20democratic%20principles%20culminated%20in%20the%20creation%20of%20this%20constitution%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20there%20are%20aspects%20that%20might%20warrant%20reconsideration.%20I%E2%80%99d%20like%20to%20emphasise%20that%20the%20constitution%E2%80%99s%20ongoing%20interpretation%20and%20application%20are%20essential%20for%20its%20relevance%20and%20effectiveness%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20for%20the%20principle%20of%20%E2%80%98one%20person%2C%20one%20vote%E2%80%99%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20indeed%20a%20fundamental%20tenet%20of%20democracy.%20However%2C%20it%20raises%20questions%20about%20how%20political%20power%2C%20derived%20from%20numerical%20representation%2C%20intersects%20with%20other%20crucial%20aspects%20like%20financial%20distribution.%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20an%20economist%2C%20but%20I%20can%20provide%20an%20example%20to%20illustrate%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20there%20are%20two%20high%20courts%20in%20India%20where%20the%20use%20of%20Hindi%20as%20a%20language%20of%20communication%20is%20legally%20permissible%20%E2%80%93%20Rajasthan%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20Other%20states%20have%20subsequently%20joined.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20development%20occurred%20in%20the%201950s%20when%20the%20assemblies%20passed%20a%20resolution%2C%20and%20the%20government%20was%20tasked%20with%20notifying%20Hindi%20as%20a%20language%20for%20high%20courts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20note%20that%20this%20decision%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20influenced%20by%20any%20particular%20political%20party.%20However%2C%20despite%20the%20resolution%2C%20the%20use%20of%20Hindi%20in%20high%20courts%20has%20not%20become%20widespread.%20This%20raises%20questions%20about%20the%20practical%20application%20of%20such%20decisions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERequest%20for%20Hindi%20in%20court%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20he%20once%20attended%20a%20gathering%20where%20the%20demand%20was%20raised%20to%20make%20Hindi%20an%20official%20language%20for%20legal%20documents%20and%20court%20proceedings.%20Many%20speakers%20supported%20this%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20it%20was%20my%20turn%2C%20I%20mentioned%20that%20I%20come%20from%20a%20region%20where%20Hindi%20is%20not%20widely%20spoken%2C%20and%20I%20had%20watched%20numerous%20Hindi%20movies.%20I%20asked%20if%20anyone%20in%20the%20audience%20had%20seen%20even%20one%20South%20Indian%20movie%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20language.%20Surprisingly%2C%20not%20a%20single%20person%20had.%20My%20point%20was%20that%20diversity%20in%20languages%20is%20important%2C%20and%20learning%20more%20languages%20is%20enriching%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%2C%20however%2C%20these%20decisions%20could%20be%20politically%20influenced.%20For%20instance%2C%20Hindi-speaking%20individuals%20formed%20a%20majority%20in%20parliament%2C%20and%20this%20influenced%20decisions%20regarding%20language%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20election%20processes%20should%20adhere%20to%20the%20constitutional%20principle%20that%20the%20ratio%20of%20representation%20among%20states%20should%20be%20roughly%20equitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fdakshin-dialogues%2Fretd-justice-chelameswar-on-delimitation-impact-should-somebody-get-a-premium-for-their-nonperformance%2F%5C%22%3Estory%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20Sou