nths%2C%20have%20vanished%20in%20the%20face%20of%20Hamas's%20slaughter%20at%20the%20weekend%20and%20fears%20the%20conflict%20could%20spread%20to%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20is%20talking%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20about%20forming%20an%20emergency%20war%20government.%20The%20protest%20movement%20opposing%20the%20government's%20efforts%20to%20weaken%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20shifted%20its%20focus%20to%20raising%20money%20and%20helping%20families%20and%20soldiers%20in%20the%20south%2C%20working%20with%20authorities%20they%20disdained.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYet%20how%20long%20the%20country%20remains%20galvanized%20behind%20what%20promises%20to%20be%20a%20grinding%20campaign%20lasting%20months%20remains%20in%20question.%20While%20Netanyahu%20will%20stay%20in%20power%2C%20the%20intelligence%20and%20security%20failures%20have%20also%20shocked%20the%20nation.%20He's%20likely%20to%20end%20up%20paying%20the%20political%20price%20for%20it%20just%20as%20Golda%20Meir%20did%20in%20the%201973%20war%20when%20Syria%20and%20Egypt%20surprised%20Israel.%20She%20stepped%20down%20in%20disgrace%20months%20later.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolitical%20differences%20are%20set%20aside%20in%20times%20of%20war%2C%20but%20Netanyahu%20might%20be%20on%20borrowed%20time%20because%20of%20the%20lapse%2C%20according%20to%20Yoel%20Esteron%2C%20founder%20and%20publisher%20of%20Israeli%20business%20daily%20Calcalist%20and%20a%20former%20media%20and%20politics%20lecturer%20in%20Tel%20Aviv.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProtests%20brought%20Meir%20down%2C%20but%20only%20after%20the%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20Esteron%20said%20on%20Monday.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20this%20will%20happen%20here.%20There%20is%20a%20good%20chance%20for%20an%20emergency%20unity%20government.%20But%20will%20it%20last%20after%20the%20war%3F%20I%20don't%20think%20so.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20challenges%20ahead%20-%20the%20campaign%20against%20Hamas%20has%20started%20by%20air%20but%20is%20likely%20to%20lead%20to%20a%20ground%20war%20-%20Israelis%20are%20focused%20less%20now%20on%20what%20went%20wrong%20and%20more%20on%20how%20to%20proceed.%20The%20investigation%20into%20why%20it%20wasn't%20prevented%20will%20follow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInternational%20scrutiny%20of%20Israel's%20response%20is%20already%20under%20way.%20United%20Nations%20Secretary-General%20Antonio%20Guterres%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20he%20was%20concerned%20by%20Israeli%20plans%20for%20a%20retaliatory%20siege%20of%20Gaza%2C%20with%20electricity%2C%20fuel%20and%20food%20supplies%20severed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F8ccd5p3_israel-hamas-war-bloomberg_625x300_10_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20reason%20talk%20of%20unity%20has%20grown%20is%20the%20fear%20that%20the%20surprise%20from%20Hamas%20will%20be%20followed%20by%20a%20similar%20assault%20from%20Hezbollah%20in%20Lebanon.%20Both%20Hamas%20and%20Hezbollah%20are%20heavily%20supported%20by%20Iran%2C%20Israel's%20main%20enemy%2C%20and%20both%20have%20thousands%20of%20missiles%20in%20underground%20launchers%2C%20some%20long%20enough%20range%20to%20reach%20Tel%20Aviv.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20growing%20concern%20that%20if%20Israel%20goes%20all%20in%20to%20Gaza%2C%20Hezbollah%20will%20take%20the%20opportunity%20to%20attack%20from%20the%20north.%20The%20Biden%20administration%20has%20sent%20the%20USS%20Gerald%20Ford%20aircraft%20carrier%20and%20accompanying%20war%20vessels%20to%20the%20Mediterranean%20to%20thwart%20any%20such%20possibilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnderstanding%20The%20Shadow%20War%20Between%20Israel%20And%20Iran%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20sheer%20scale%20and%20brutality%20of%20the%20attack%20has%20unified%20the%20entire%20nation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Joshua%20Hantman%2C%20a%20former%20government%20official%20and%20now%20a%20public%20relations%20executive%20and%20protest%20activist.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20spent%20the%20last%20two%20days%20watching%20videos%20of%20kids%20being%20kidnapped%20and%20of%20summary%20executions%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Israel.%20You%20don't%20forget%20that%20in%20a%20hurry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20came%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20Sabbath%20and%20a%20Jewish%20holiday.%20As%202%2C000%20rockets%20and%20missiles%20flew%20into%20Israeli%20cities%2C%20setting%20cars%20and%20houses%20alight%2C%201%2C000%20fighters%20from%20Hamas%20group%20cut%20through%20the%20border%20fence%2C%20crossed%20into%20Israel%20via%20paragliders%2C%20motorbikes%20and%20boats.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFootage%20showed%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20slaughter%2C%20including%20several%20hundred%20young%20people%20at%20an%20outdoor%20music%20festival.%20Those%20they%20didn't%20kill%20were%20grabbed%20as%20hostages%2C%20according%20to%20eyewitnesses%20speaking%20to%20Israeli%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20went%20from%20house%20to%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20Danny%20Fuchs%20of%20Kibbutz%20Beeri%2C%20a%20settlement%20just%20east%20of%20Gaza%2C%20told%20Yedioth%20Ahronoth%20newspaper%20on%20Monday.%20%26quot%3BThey%20went%20into%20the%20bomb%20shelters%20and%20either%20kidnapped%20people%20or%20killed%20them.%20Sometimes%20they%20killed%20everyone.%20Sometimes%20they%20took%20the%20children%20and%20killed%20the%20parents%2C%20or%20the%20other%20way%20around.%20We%20have%20an%20attic%20in%20our%20home%20and%20shut%20ourselves%20inside.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F8sasappo_israel-hamas-war-bloomberg_625x300_10_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20after%20the%20attack%2C%20there%20were%20still%20a%20few%20families%20marooned%20inside%20their%20homes%20in%20southern%20Israel%20with%20Hamas%20fighters%20preventing%20them%20from%20leaving.%20Talk%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%20is%20of%20Hamas%20fighters%20finding%20their%20way%20north%20and%20hiding%20in%20the%20city.%20There%20are%20some%20100%20Israelis%2C%20from%20toddlers%20to%20elderly%20women%2C%20who've%20been%20taken%20into%20Gaza%20as%20hostages.%20One%20group%2C%20Islamic%20Jihad%2C%20says%20it's%20holding%2030%20of%20them%20until%20their%20prisoners%20held%20by%20Israel%20are%20released.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20a%20long%20history%20of%20protecting%20its%20soldiers%20and%20civilians%20when%20held%20in%20enemy%20hands%20and%20returning%20many%20prisoners%20to%20get%20them%20home.%20But%20the%20fury%20seems%20so%20great%20just%20now%20that%20military%20analysts%20say%20the%20hostages%20could%20become%20victims%20of%20the%20attack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20should%20say%20no%20to%20negotiations%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20General%20Yaakov%20Amidror%2C%20a%20former%20National%20Security%20Adviser%20to%20Netanyahu.%20%26quot%3BIsrael%20cannot%20negotiate%20about%20them.%26quot%3B%20A%20senior%20Israeli%20official%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20there%20were%20no%20such%20discussions%20under%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELate%20Monday%2C%20a%20Hamas%20spokesman%20said%20on%20broadcaster%20Al%20Jazeera%20that%20if%20Israel%20struck%20civilian%20buildings%20without%20warning%2C%20the%20group%20would%20kill%20an%20Israeli%20hostage%20every%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fr4cl0hbg_israel-hamas-war-bloomberg_625x300_10_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EImpoverished%20Gaza%20has%20long%20been%20a%20flashpoint%20of%20conflict.%20Unlike%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20which%20is%20overseen%20by%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20that%20has%20negotiated%20with%20Israel%20over%20a%20two-state%20solution%2C%20Gaza%20is%20run%20by%20Hamas%2C%20which%20rejects%20Israel's%20right%20to%20exist.%20That%20caused%20difficulty%20with%20nations%20seeking%20to%20send%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%2016%20years%20of%20its%20control%2C%20Hamas%20initially%20established%20a%20network%20of%20charities%20to%20tackle%20poverty%20and%20build%20infrastructure%20with%20the%20backing%20of%20countries%20such%20as%20Qatar.%20It%20also%20fought%20half%20a%20dozen%20major%20confrontations%20with%20Israel%2C%20firing%20thousands%20of%20rockets%20at%20its%20towns%20while%20the%20Israeli%20military%20has%20repeatedly%20bombed%20the%20strip%20and%20killed%20thousands.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20plans%20for%20taking%20out%20the%20Hamas%20infrastructure%20are%20being%20presented%20as%20ending%20the%20possibility%20the%20group%20could%20ever%20attack%20Israel%20ever.%20The%20crowded%20Gaza%20Strip%20will%20be%20bombarded%3B%20civilian%20casualties%20will%20be%20extensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlready%2C%20some%20560%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed.%20Israel%20is%20hitting%20buildings%20in%20populated%20areas%2C%20making%20it%20hard%20for%20residents%20to%20find%20safety.%20%26quot%3BGaza%20will%20be%20under%20complete%20closure%2C%26quot%3B%20Defense%20Minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20told%20troops%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELieutenant%20Colonel%20Richard%20Hecht%2C%20a%20spokesman%20for%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%2C%20declined%20to%20say%20if%20there%20would%20be%20alerts%20to%20residents%20in%20Gaza%20before%20bombing.%20Responding%20to%20a%20question%20at%20a%20briefing%20on%20Monday%2C%20he%20said%20this%20is%20war%20and%20Hamas%20group%20who%20entered%20Israel%20on%20Saturday%20felt%20no%20need%20to%20offer%20a%20warning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUntil%20Saturday%2C%20the%2073-year-old%20Netanyahu%20-%20although%20comfortably%20in%20power%20with%20a%20ruling%20majority%20made%20up%20of%20religious%20and%20right-wing%20parties%20-%20was%20in%20political%20trouble%20for%20his%20populist%20policies%2C%20causing%20the%20street%20demonstrations.%20But%20he%20also%20seemed%20on%20the%20way%20to%20possible%20political%20redemption%2C%20sealing%20a%20complex%20deal%20with%20the%20US%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20for%20Saudi%20normalization%20of%20relations%20with%20Israel%20in%20exchange%20for%20US%20security%20guarantees%20for%20Riyadh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThose%20talks%20will%20be%20on%20hold%20as%20Israel%20puts%20all%20its%20efforts%20into%20the%20military%20campaign.%20Whether%20they%20will%20then%20be%20revived%20-%20with%20or%20without%20Netanyahu%20-%20is%20hard%20to%20say.%20Both%20the%20US%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20want%20the%20deal%20to%20proceed.%20But%20when%20the%20area%20is%20aflame%20in%20combat%2C%20it%20can't.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20will%20be%20countervailing%20pressures%20from%20the%20war%20with%20Hamas.%20If%20it%20drags%20on%20and%20many%20people%20die%2C%20Arab%20public%20opinion%20will%20make%20it%20hard%20for%20the%20Saudi%20leadership%20to%20return%20to%20the%20talks.%20But%20if%20Israel%20wins%20relatively%20quickly%2C%20some%20analysts%20think%20that%20will%20ultimately%20help%20the%20deal%20proceed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDomestically%2C%20the%20government%20is%20taking%20fierce%20criticism%20for%20claiming%20that%20it%20was%20doing%20a%20better%20job%20than%20others%20at%20keeping%20the%20country%20safe.%20Some%20have%20said%20that%20Netanyahu's%20focus%20on%20protecting%20and%20promoting%20Jewish%20settlements%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20led%20it%20to%20base%20more%20troops%20there%20and%20not%20enough%20near%20Gaza.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELike%20the%201973%20war%2C%20the%20failure%20to%20anticipate%20the%20attack%20is%20also%20viewed%20as%20a%20conceptual%20one%20-%20the%20widespread%20belief%20that%20the%20enemy%20was%20too%20timid%20or%20deterred%20to%20dare%20attack.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Hamas%2C%20its%20leadership%20spent%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20years%20giving%20the%20impression%20of%20seeking%20to%20be%20more%20of%20a%20governing%20body%20in%20Gaza%20and%20less%20of%20a%20fighting%20force.%20It%20stayed%20out%20of%20several%20recent%20skirmishes%20between%20Israel%20and%20Islamic%20Jihad%2C%20focusing%20on%20job%20opportunities%20in%20Israel%20for%20Gazans.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20now%20a%20fresh%20war%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20it%20isn't%20clear%20whether%20Hamas%20was%20planning%20all%20along%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20attack.%20It%20may%20have%20been%20inspired%20only%20recently%20to%20try%20and%20block%20the%20Saudi%20deal%20-%20which%20might%20have%20left%20the%20Palestinians%20in%20the%20cold%20-%20and%20take%20advantage%20of%20internal%20Israeli%20divisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20not%20clear%20how%20strong%20an%20influence%20Iran%20had.%20The%20Islamic%20Republic%20leads%20the%20anti-American%20and%20anti-Israeli%20forces%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20has%20recently%20decided%20to%20invest%20effort%20in%20supporting%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20according%20to%20Amos%20Yadlin%2C%20a%20former%20director%20of%20Israeli%20military%20intelligence.%20Iran%20finances%20Hezbollah%20with%20%241%20billion%20a%20year%20and%20Hamas%20with%20%24100%20million%2C%20said%20Yadlin.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWithin%20Israel%2C%20the%20attack%20has%20effectively%20ended%20the%20protest%20movement%20for%20now.%20Lee%20Moser%2C%20a%20venture%20capitalist%20who%20volunteers%20to%20help%20run%20Brothers%20and%20Sisters%20in%20Arms%2C%20an%20organization%20with%20more%20than%201%20million%20members%20that%20led%20demonstrations%2C%20said%20her%20group%20has%20switched%20to%20helping%20the%20war%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoser%20said%20she%20raised%20%2410%20million%20in%20five%20hours%20for%20equipment%20and%20supplies%2C%20and%20has%20many%20millions%20more%20being%20offered.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20working%20with%20the%20government%20and%20the%20army%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20understands%20that%20to%20win%20this%2C%20we%20need%20to%20stick%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPoliticians%20across%20the%20spectrum%20are%20also%20weighing%20in.%20Opposition%20leader%20Benny%20Gantz%20said%20on%20Monday%20it%20was%20time%20to%20unite%20and%20%26quot%3Bemerge%20victorious.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%2C%20who%20has%20run%20Israel%20for%20longer%20than%20any%20other%20prime%20minister%20and%20is%20now%20in%20his%20sixth%20government%2C%20hasn't%20yet%20announced%20a%20unity%20deal.%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20his%20coalition%20partners%20said%20they'd%20agreed%20to%20form%20an%20emergency%20administration%20with%20the%20opposition%20and%20authorized%20Netanyahu%20to%20do%20so.%20The%20betting%20is%20that%20some%20version%20of%20one%20will%20emerge.%20And%20equally%2C%20that%20this%20will%20be%20his%20last.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696949820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fpcrpgsio_israel-army-reuters-_625x300_10_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbrutality-of-surprise-attack-unites-israel-around-one-goal-crush-hamas-4468461%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20normally%20bustling%20streets%20of%20Tel%20Aviv%20are%20empty%2C%20schools%20shut%2C%20flights%20canceled%20and%20a%20major%20gas%20field%20closed.%20Men%20of%20all%20ages%20are%20getting%20called%20to%20their%20reserve%20units%2C%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20throwing%20on%20uniforms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbrutality-of-surprise-attack-unites-israel-around-one-goal-crush-hamas-4468461%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3