20He%20highlighted%20that%20this%20data%20will%20provide%20insights%20into%20factors%20like%20education%2C%20land%20ownership%2C%20and%20economic%20status%20within%20different%20castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20the%20survey%20results%20could%20have%20a%20cascading%20effect%20across%20states%20and%20pose%20an%20electoral%20dilemma%20for%20the%20BJP%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20elections%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReproduced%20below%20is%20the%20full%20transcript%20of%20the%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESravasti%20Dasgupta%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20%3Cstrong%3EHello%20and%20welcome%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%20I%E2%80%99m%20Sravasti%20Dasgupta.%20On%20October%202%2C%20the%20Bihar%20government%20released%20caste%20survey%20data.%20According%20to%20the%20data%2C%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%2C%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SCs)%2C%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(STs)%20constitute%20about%2084%25%20of%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20while%20the%20Forward%20Caste%20or%20the%20General%20Category%2C%20as%20they%20are%20known%2C%20is%20only%2015.5%25.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETo%20discuss%20the%20implications%20of%20the%20caste%20survey%20data%20on%20the%20national%20politics%2C%20and%20what%20it%20really%20means%2C%20we%20have%20with%20us%20today%20Yogendra%20Yadav%2C%20who%20is%20an%20activist%2C%20psephologist%2C%20and%20founder%20of%20the%20Swaraj%20Abhiyan%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThank%20you%20so%20much%20Mr.%20Yadav%20for%20joining%20us%20on%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EYogendra%20Yadav%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EThank%20you%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESravasti%20Dasgupta%3A%20My%20first%20question%20is%2C%20since%20the%20last%20caste%20census%2C%20which%20was%20conducted%20in%201931%20by%20the%20British%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%2010%25%20jump%20in%20the%20%5Bpopulation%20of%20the%20Economically%20Backward%20Castes%5D%20EBCs%20and%20the%20OBC%20groups%2C%20as%20we%20can%20see%20in%20this%20data.%20I%20want%20to%20mention%20to%20our%20viewers%20that%20the%201931%20census%20was%2C%20of%20course%2C%20conducted%20during%20the%20British%20in%20an%20undivided%20India.%20Mr.%20Yadav%2C%20how%20do%20you%20see%20these%20figures%20which%20show%20a%2010%25%20jump%2C%20and%20also%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Forward%20Castes%20are%20a%20mere%2015.5%25.%20How%20one%20must%20see%20this%20data%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EYogendra%20Yadav%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3ESravasti%2C%20I%20think%20we%20must%20tell%20our%20viewers%20what%20this%20whole%20thing%20%5Bcaste%20survey%5D%20is%20all%20about%2C%20and%20how%20%E2%80%98not%20to%E2%80%99%20read%20this%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20only%20received%20the%20first%20installment%20of%20the%20caste%20survey%20data%20in%20Bihar.%20So%20far%2C%20it%20shows%20only%20the%20population%20numbers%2C%20%5Bmeaning%5D%20which%20caste%20has%20how%20much%20proportion%20in%20the%20population.%20This%20is%20only%20the%20first%20and%20the%20less%20significant%20part%20of%20the%20data%20for%20the%20caste%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20real%20significant%20part%20of%20this%20data%20is%20yet%20to%20come.%20This%20would%20be%20the%20data%20on%20the%20socio-economic%20profile%20of%20each%20of%20these%20castes%20%E2%80%93%20how%20many%20of%20them%20are%20graduates%20in%20each%20caste%3B%20how%20many%20of%20them%20have%20four-wheelers%2C%20a%20laptop%3B%20how%20many%20of%20them%20are%20engaged%20in%20agriculture%20labour%3B%20how%20much%20land%20do%20they%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20the%20real%20figures%20that%20I%E2%80%99m%20really%20looking%20forward%20to.%20What%20we%20have%20so%20far%20is%20only%20the%20population%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20surprises%2C%20and%20%5Balso%5D%20not%20much%20for%20those%20people%20like%20me%20who%20have%20been%20following%20surveys%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20must%20also%20remember%20that%20normally%2C%20the%20census%20takes%20place%20in%20the%20country%20every%20ten%20years.%20It%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20happened%20since%202021%2C%20%5Bwhich%20is%5D%20an%20extraordinary%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Census%20of%20India%20not%20only%20tells%20us%20the%20total%20population%2C%20but%20gives%20us%20the%20population%20of%20%5Bthe%20persons%20belonging%20to%5D%20the%20SC%2C%20ST%20%5Bcommunities%5D%2C%20and%20the%20religious%20population%2C%20including%20that%20of%20the%20Muslims.%20This%20is%20the%20novel%20thing%2C%20so%20the%20idea%20that%20we%20know%20nothing%20about%20the%20castes%20of%20India%20since%201931%20is%20completely%20false.%20We%20do%20know%20certain%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20additional%20things%20that%20we%20know%20because%20of%20this%20survey%20are%20the%20number%20of%20OBCs%20within%20the%20OBCs%2C%20the%20number%20of%20upper%20OBCs%20or%20the%20backward%2C%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98lower%E2%80%99%20OBCs%2C%20the%20extremely%20backward.%20These%20are%20the%20new%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20the%20survey%20has%20told%20us%20is%20the%20following%3A%20it%20has%2C%20of%20course%2C%20updated%20the%20overall%20population%20of%20Bihar%2C%20which%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20known%20because%20we%20haven%E2%80%99t%20had%20a%20%5Bcaste%5D%20survey%20or%20a%20census%20for%20the%20last%2030%20years.%20It%20tells%20us%20that%20the%20proportion%20of%20SCs%2C%20STs%2C%20and%20Muslims%20has%20gone%20up.%20The%20growth%20in%20the%20case%20of%20SCs%20and%20STs%20is%20substantial%20and%20very%20steep.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Muslims%2C%20the%20growth%20is%20not%20so%20steep.%20It%20tells%20us%20that%20the%20proportion%20of%20OBCs%20is%20much%20bigger%20than%20what%20was%20normally%20imagined.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESomehow%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20been%20a%20mythical%20figure%20of%2052%25%20floating%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20Bihar%2C%20now%20we%20know%20the%20overall%20proportion%20of%20the%20OBCs%20is%2063%25%2C%20which%20is%20higher%20than%20the%20NSSO%20estimates%20and%20other%20estimates%20that%20we%20have%20known.%20What%20we%20also%20know%20is%20that%20within%20the%20OBCs%2C%20it%20is%20the%20EBCs%2C%20the%20extremely%20backward%20castes%2C%20which%20are%20not%20spoken%20about%2C%20who%20no%20one%20notices%2C%20who%20get%20very%20little%20representation%20in%20politics%20and%20in%20other%20positions%20of%20power.%20They%20comprise%2037%25.%20So%2C%20these%2C%20I%20believe%2C%20are%20the%20important%20findings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20also%20know%20is%20the%20relative%20proportion%20of%20each%20caste%20and%20community.%20You%20have%20mentioned%20that%20the%20forward%20castes%20are%2015.5%25.%20I%20think%20we%20need%20to%20nuance%20it%20further%20because%20these%20forward%20castes%20also%20include%20some%20Muslims%2C%20the%20Sheikhs%2C%20Syeds%2C%20Pathans%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20four%20Hindu%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20castes%2C%20which%20are%20the%20real%20privileged%20communities%20of%20Bihar%2C%20namely%20the%20Brahmins%2C%20Bhumihars%2C%20Rajputs%2C%20and%20Kayasthas%2C%20put%20together%2C%20make%20up%20only%2010.6%25%20of%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20a%20staggering%20figure%2C%20because%20so%20much%20of%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20public%20life%20used%20to%20be%20controlled%2C%20and%20is%20still%20dominated%2C%20by%20these%20four%20communities%2C%20which%20comprise%20only%2010.6%25.%20So%20one-tenth%20of%20Bihar%20controls%20so%20much%20of%20public%20life.%20That%20is%20an%20important%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FjT3WLZ828mY%3Fsi%3DKT-Yo-knXV5tW9qw%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAt%20the%20moment%2C%20this%20data%20does%20not%20give%20out%20the%20socio-economic%20conditions%20of%20these%20castes.%20Note%20that%20the%20Bihar%20government%20has%20said%20that%20it%20will%20be%20releasing%20this%20data%20very%20soon.%20However%2C%20this%20is%20being%20used%20as%20an%20opportunity%20by%20many%20in%20the%20opposition%20to%20claim%20that%20we%20cannot%20say%20anything%20about%20the%20data%20at%20the%20moment%20because%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cincomplete%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20the%20absence%20of%20this%20socio-economic%20data%2C%20how%20should%20we%20interpret%20the%20current%20data%2C%20because%20the%20idea%20behind%20releasing%20this%20data%20was%20to%20discuss%20development.%20But%20without%20the%20numbers%2C%20how%20can%20we%20deliver%20the%20goods%20of%20development%3F%20So%2C%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20this%20socio-economic%20data%2C%20how%20one%20must%20read%20the%20current%20data%20that%20we%20have%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESravasti%2C%20the%20word%20%E2%80%9Cincomplete%E2%80%9D%20is%20misleading.%20The%20data%20is%20not%20incomplete.%20The%20data%20which%20has%20been%20put%20out%20is%20complete%2C%20reliable%2C%20and%20final.%20There%20is%20nothing%20provisional%2C%20temporary%2C%20or%20uncertain%20about%20the%20data%3B%20it%20is%20incomplete%20only%20in%20the%20second%20sense.%20That%20means%20there%20are%20other%20sets%20of%20information%20yet%20to%20be%20released.%20This%20is%20exactly%20how%20big%20survey%20data%20is%20always%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYou%20first%20release%20the%20population%20totals%20and%20then%20you%20release%20tables%20on%20specific%20social%20backgrounds.%20So%2C%20the%20second%20set%20of%20data%20is%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20know%20right%20now%20is%20the%20proportion%20of%20each%20%3Cem%3Ejaati%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20each%20social%20group.%20What%20we%20do%20not%20officially%20know%20yet%20is%20what%20proportion%20of%20land%20does%20each%20community%20control%2C%20how%20much%20educational%20advantages%20and%20privileges%20they%20enjoy.%20We%20do%20have%20some%20sense%20about%20these%20things%20because%20NSSO%20has%20been%20looking%20at%20these%20things%2C%20and%20I%20looked%20at%20the%20previous%20NSSO%20reports%2C%20they%20gave%20a%20very%20broad%20idea%20%5Bon%20this%20matter%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20we%20do%20know%20from%20the%20NSSO%20%5Bdata%5D%20is%20that%20among%20those%20who%20have%2C%20say%2C%20five%20acres%20of%20land%20or%20above%2C%20which%20is%20a%20substantially%20big%20proportion%20of%20land%20among%20them%2C%20there%20is%20a%20huge%20difference%20between%20the%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20caste%20Hindus%20and%20the%20OBCs.%20Only%209.2%25%20of%20the%20general%20category%20were%20%5Bengaged%20in%5D%20agricultural%20labour%20while%20for%20the%20OBCs%2C%20it%20is%2029%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20NSSO%20official%20data%2C%20not%20the%20Bihar%20census%2C%20right%20now%2C%20gives%20you%20a%20broad%20idea%20of%20land%20ownership%20among%20those%20who%20control%20five%20acres%20or%20more%20land.%20It%20is%20twice%20as%20much%20among%20the%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20castes%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20OBCs.%20In%20education%2C%20only%2010.5%25%20of%20the%20general%20category%20%5Bpopulation%5D%20were%20graduates.%20Among%20the%20OBCs%2C%20the%20proportion%20was%20only%202.8%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20we%20should%20expect%20to%20see%20stark%20differences%20between%20these%20categories.%20We%20should%20also%20expect%20to%20see%20stark%20differences%20within%20these%20categories%2C%20because%20OBC%20is%20an%20umbrella%20category.%20It%20includes%20both%20landed%20and%20somewhat%20powerful%20communities%20like%20the%20Yadavs%20and%20Koeris%2C%20but%20it%20also%20includes%20service%20and%20landless%2C%20and%20very%20small%20communities%2C%20which%20have%2C%20say%2C%20very%20little%20power%2C%20very%20little%20education%2C%20and%20some%20of%20them%20are%20worse%20off%20than%20Dalits.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20that%20is%20the%20profile%20we%20are%20likely%20to%20get.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%2C%20incidentally%2C%20also%20the%20first%20survey%20in%20Bihar%20which%20has%20given%20us%20a%20detailed%20breakup%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20Within%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20only%203%25%20to%204%25%20are%20privileged%2C%20forward%2C%20and%20the%20remaining%2C%20about%2014%25%20are%20backward.%20So%2C%20the%20real%20advantage%20of%20this%20survey%20is%20that%20it%20has%20put%20the%20focus%20on%20the%20most%20disadvantaged%20invisibilised%20micro%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20an%20important%20point%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20data%20has%20put%20the%20focus%20on%20the%20most%20invisibilised%20sections%20of%20our%20community.%20You%20had%20also%20mentioned%20earlier%20that%20one-tenth%20of%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20population%20is%20controlling%20the%20goods%20of%20development.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENote%20that%20in%202019%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Ften-per-cent-reservation-economically-weaker-upper-caste-modi-government-1425241-2019-01-07%5C%22%3Egave%3C%2Fa%3E%2010%25%20reservations%20for%20the%20economically%20weaker%20sections.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20upheld%20this%20reservation%20and%20waived%20off%20the%2050%25%20ceiling%2C%20which%20is%20the%20national%20cap%20on%20caste-based%20reservations.%20Now%20with%20these%20new%20figures%20coming%20in%2C%20do%20you%20think%20it%20is%20viable%20to%20defend%2010%25%20for%20about%2015%25%20of%20the%20population%20and%2027%25%20for%20over%2060%25%20of%20the%20population%3F%20How%20can%20one%20defend%20this%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESravasti%2C%20this%20actually%20puts%20the%20focus%20on%20something%20utterly%20ridiculous%2C%20something%20that%20we%E2%80%99ve%20already%20mentioned%2C%20and%20for%20this%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20socio-economic%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%20we%20know%20that%20there%20is%20a%20group%20in%20Bihar%20which%20is%2015.5%25.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20include%20the%20Muslim%20Sheikhs%20and%20Pathans%20here%20as%20well%2C%20because%20technically%2C%20they%20%5Bcome%20under%20the%5D%20non-reserved%20%5Bcategory%5D.%20So%2C%20about%2015.5%25%20%5Bof%20the%20population%5D%20are%20unreserved%2C%20generally%2C%20of%20which%20there%20are%20people%20who%20are%20economically%20weaker.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20many%2C%20no%20one%20has%20conducted%20a%20survey%2C%20no%20one%20knows%20the%20numbers%2C%20%5Band%5D%20who%20have%20been%20given%20a%2010%25%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20a%20slice%20of%20the%2015%25%2C%20presumably%2C%20a%20slice%20which%20would%20be%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20say%2C%20half%2C%20%5Bor%5D%20less%20than%20half%2C%20so%207%20to%208%25%20have%20been%20given%2010%25%20reservation.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%2063%25%20of%20the%20population%20has%20central%20government%20jobs%2C%20and%20has%2027%25%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Bihar%20government%2C%20they%20have%2030%25%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20include%20women%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20little%20more%20than%2030%25%20reservation%2C%20but%20that%E2%80%99s%20still%20less%20than%20half%2C%20so%20there%E2%80%99s%20something%20absurd%20that%20we%20are%20looking%20at.%20And%2C%20in%20a%20sense%2C%20the%20EWS%20reservation%20appears%20to%20be%20an%20extra%20reward%20for%20those%20who%20are%20already%20privileged.%20%5BThat%5D%20makes%20no%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20must%20say%20I%20was%20utterly%20surprised%20and%20disappointed%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20judgment.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20written%20about%20that.%20I%20really%20wish%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20asked%20for%20the%20data%2C%20as%20it%20has%20done%20in%20every%20other%20case.%20It%E2%80%99s%20only%20in%20the%20case%20of%20EWS%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20suddenly%20said%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20need%20for%20data%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20look%20at%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20every%20other%20case%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20asked%2C%20demanded%2C%20insisted%2C%20that%20we%20must%20have%20evidence%20before%20we%20can%20provide%20any%20quota.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20they%20did%20not%20and%20the%20results%20are%20now%20quite%20obvious%20in%20our%20face.%20This%20is%20absurd.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20mentioning%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20absurd%20that%20a%20very%20small%20section%20of%20the%20population%2C%20as%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Bihar%2C%20about%2015.5%25%2C%20get%20additional%20reservation%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20economically%20weaker%20sections%20quota.%20But%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20about%20the%20politics%20surrounding%20the%20caste%20survey.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20opposition%20parties%20have%20been%20united%20in%20their%20chorus%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20at%20the%20national%20level.%20The%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20has%20also%20found%20unanimous%20support%20among%20members%20of%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance.%20Meanwhile%2C%20we%20have%20not%20seen%20a%20very%20coherent%20response%20from%20the%20BJP.%20The%20prime%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fbihar-caste-survey-pm-modi-reaction-opposition-trying-to-divide-country-2443575-2023-10-03%5C%22%3Ereleased%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20statement%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20ago%20where%20he%20accused%20the%20opposition%20of%20attempting%20to%20divide%20the%20country%2C%20but%20we%E2%80%99ll%20come%20to%20that%20in%20just%20a%20moment.%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20you%2C%20%5Bconsidering%20that%5D%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20vote%20share%20from%20the%20OBC%20community%20was%20about%2044%25%20in%202019%2C%20how%20do%20you%20see%20this%20resonating%20in%20the%20upcoming%20general%20elections%20next%20year%3F%20With%20the%20chorus%20from%20the%20opposition%20parties%20about%20social%20justice%2C%20do%20you%20think%20it%20will%20find%20some%20resonance%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFirst%20thing%20first%20Sravasti%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20political%20benefits%2C%20this%20is%20a%20step%20forward.%20If%20the%20BJP%20benefits%20from%20it%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20step%20forward.%20If%20the%20opposition%20benefits%20from%20it%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20step%20forward.%20Getting%20to%20know%20the%20truth%20about%20our%20society%2C%20getting%20an%20X-ray%20of%20the%20social%20situation%20in%20our%20society%20is%20definitely%20a%20step%20forward%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20political%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20who%20would%20gain%20from%20it%2C%20it%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20simple%20equation%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20caste%20votes%2C%20and%20the%20opposition%20has%20the%20OBC%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20that%20was%20the%20case%2C%20the%20BJP%20would%20be%20nowhere%20in%20Bihar%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20does%20have%20a%20significant%20proportion%20of%20OBC%20votes%2C%20especially%20the%20%5Bvotes%20from%20the%5D%20EBCs.%20This%20survey%20puts%20the%20focus%20on%20that.%20So%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20necessary%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20be%20disadvantaged%20by%20this%20%5Bsurvey%5D.%20That%20is%20probably%20the%20reason%20why%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Bihar%20leadership%20wants%20to%20be%20seen%20to%20be%20supporting%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20at%20a%20larger%20national%20level%2C%20if%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20gathers%20ground%2C%20it%20can%20have%20a%20cascading%20effect.%20Bihar%20has%20released%20it%2C%20Odisha%20says%20they%20are%20about%20to%20release%20it%2C%20Karnataka%20government%20is%20sitting%20on%20it%20and%20they%20can%20release%20it%20any%20day.%20They%20just%20need%20a%20nod%20from%20the%20Delhi%20Congress%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnine-reasons-why-the-bihar-caste-census-could-shake-up-national-politics%5C%22%3ENine%20Reasons%20Why%20Numbers%20Revealed%20by%20Bihar%20Caste%20Census%20Could%20Shake%20up%20National%20Politics%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20BJP%20is%20seen%20to%20be%20opposing%20it%2C%20then%20it%20will%20come%20across%20as%20not%20a%20friend%20of%20the%20OBC%2C%20because%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20is%20seen%20to%20be%20a%20demand%20for%20the%20recognition%20of%20the%20OBC%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20is%20simple.%20The%20SCs%20and%20STs%20are%20already%20being%20counted.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20OBC%20community%20which%20is%20not%20being%20counted.%20So%2C%20if%20the%20BJP%20seems%20to%20be%20opposing%20the%20caste%20census%20demand%2C%20%5Band%20it%20is%20currently%20opposing%20this%20demand%5D%2C%20and%20if%20the%20demand%20gathers%20ground%2C%20then%20it%20can%20lead%20to%20a%20mobilisation%20of%20the%20OBCs%20against%20the%20BJP.%20That%20is%20what%20it%20fears%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20its%20is%20attempting%20to%20counter%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20suspect%20that%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20arrests%2C%20detentions%2C%20and%20raids%20on%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5Bmay%20be%20related%20to%5D%20the%20government%20being%20so%20afraid%20of%20the%20publicity%20that%20the%20Bihar%20survey%20was%20getting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%5BI%20am%20building%5D%20on%20your%20point%20that%20the%20Bihar%20leadership%20of%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20cautious%20in%20their%20approach%20to%20the%20caste%20survey%20data.%20While%20we%20have%20had%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20saying%2C%20at%20a%20rally%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20ago%2C%20that%20the%20opposition%20is%20trying%20to%20divide%20the%20country%2C%20Bihar%20BJP%20leaders%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-narendra-modi-social-justice-caste-census-obc-dalit%5C%22%3Ehave%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20different%20things%20at%20different%20points.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBihar%20BJP%20chief%20Samrat%20Chaudhary%20said%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20read%20this%20data%20and%20go%20through%20it%20thoroughly%20before%20coming%20up%20with%20anything%2C%20or%20Giriraj%20Singh%2C%20who%20said%20that%20Nitish%20Kumar%20is%20trying%20to%20mislead%20people.%20So%2C%20we%20have%20got%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20statements%20coming%20in%2C%20or%20in%20fact%2C%20someone%20like%20Sushil%20Kumar%20Modi%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbihar-caste-census-bjp-india-bloc%5C%22%3Ehas%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20was%20the%20BJP%20which%20started%20the%20process%20of%20the%20caste%20survey%20in%20Bihar.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%2C%20right%20now%2C%20the%20BJP%20appears%20to%20lack%20a%20coherent%20position%20on%20this%20matter.%20Do%20you%20think%20this%20non-conformist%20approach%20will%20be%20beneficial%20than%20taking%20a%20%5Bclear%5D%20yes%20or%20no%20stance%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20merely%20the%20prime%20minister.%20I%20think%20the%20dilemma%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20caught%20in%20is%20much%20deeper.%20As%20we%20all%20know%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20RSS%20would%20like%20to%20see%20the%20end%20of%20reservations%20in%20this%20country.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20like%20reservation%20for%20SCs%20and%20STs%2C%20and%20they%20certainly%20do%20not%20want%20an%20expansion%20and%20extension%20of%20the%20caste-based%20reservation%20social%20justice%20apparatus.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20given%20the%20logic%20of%20elections%20and%20numbers%2C%20they%20do%20not%20want%20to%20be%20seen%20to%20be%20opposing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERemember%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20merely%20the%20recent%20things%E2%80%A6you%E2%80%99ve%20correctly%20pointed%20out%20all%20the%20recent%20contradictions%2C%20but%20these%20contradictions%20go%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20joined%20the%20unanimous%20chorus%20in%20parliament%20to%20demand%20a%20caste-based%20census.%20A%20resolution%20was%20passed%20in%20parliament%20in%202010.%20The%20BJP%20had%20happily%20endorsed%20it.%20%5BIt%20said%5D%20there%20should%20be%20a%20caste-based%20census.%20In%202018%2C%20when%20Mr.%20Rajnath%20Singh%20was%20the%20home%20minister%2C%20he%20had%20given%20an%20assurance%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20House%20that%20in%20the%20next%20census%2C%20OBCs%20shall%20be%20counted.%20This%20demand%20has%20been%20made%20by%20the%20parliamentary%20committee%20dominated%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20demand%20has%20been%20made%20by%20six%20governments%2C%20not%20one%20or%20two%2C%20and%20this%20is%20something%20which%20has%20been%20endorsed%20by%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Backward%20Classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20merely%20one%20source%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20merely%20the%20Bihar%20BJP.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20larger%20national%20dilemma.%20And%20if%20this%20demand%20gathers%20ground%2C%20the%20BJP%20would%20have%20to%20come%20clean.%20It%20would%20have%20to%20take%20one%20side.%20And%20with%20the%20prime%20minister%20already%20taking%20this%20side%2C%20there%20are%20not%20too%20many%20sides%20the%20BJP%20can%20take.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20they%20have%20not%20allowed%20caste%20census%20to%20be%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20clearly%20on%20the%20wrong%20side%20of%20this%20movement%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20it%20would%20not%20want%20this%20%5Bnews%5D%20to%20gather%20pace%2C%20to%20become%20a%20demand%2C%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20something%20which%20is%20endorsed%20by%20the%20OBC%20%5Bcommunity%5D%2C%20and%20hence%2C%20its%20desperate%20attempt%20to%20somehow%20just%20cover%20this%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-nda-allies-caste-census%5C%22%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20NDA%20Allies%20Sing%20a%20Different%20Tune%2C%20Reiterate%20Demand%20for%20Caste%20Census%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20were%20mentioning%20that%20historically%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20RSS%20have%20sought%20to%20do%20away%20with%20caste-based%20reservations%20in%20India.%20However%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20observed%20a%20departure%20in%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20point%20of%20view%20recently.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMr.%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-politics%2Frss-mohan-bhagawat-reservations-8929452%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20would%20not%20oppose%20caste-based%20reservations%2C%20which%20makes%20a%20departure%20from%20his%20earlier%20view%20expressed%20in%202015%2C%20where%20he%20said%20that%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20reevaluated.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20the%20current%20political%20climate%20where%20the%20BJP%20is%20targeting%20the%20opposition%20and%20emphasising%20%E2%80%98sanatan%20dharma%E2%80%99%20as%20a%20focal%20point%20of%20its%20attack%2C%20do%20you%20think%20it%20will%20be%20challenging%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20disregard%20the%20caste%20divisions%20that%20%E2%80%98sanatan%20dharma%E2%80%99%20inherently%20propagates%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20really%20depends%20on%20how%20the%20opposition%20plays%20it.%20If%20the%20opposition%20succeeds%20in%20making%20this%20into%20a%20big%20question%2C%20%5Bespecially%5D%20if%20%5Bother%20states%20such%20as%5D%20Odisha%20and%20Karnataka%20follow%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20lead%2C%20and%20Rajasthan%20has%20already%20declared%2C%20but%20probably%20not%20notified%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20caste%20census.%20So%2C%20if%20there%20is%20a%20cascading%20effect%2C%20then%20the%20BJP%20is%20caught.%20Then%20they%20will%20have%20to%20take%20a%20position%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20the%20BJP%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20this%20demand%20to%20come%20up%2C%20because%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20positions%20to%20take.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20it%20depends%20on%20how%20the%20opposition%20plays%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20can%20truly%20be%20a%20very%20important%20moment%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202024%20%5BLok%20Sabha%20elections%5D.%20The%20BJP%20knows%20it%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%2C%20probably%2C%20the%20RSS%20chief%20was%20persuaded%20to%20issue%20the%20statement%20%5Bon%20caste%20reservations%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEveryone%20knows%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20position%20on%20this%20issue.%20This%20is%20something%20they%20are%20deeply%20uncomfortable%20with%2C%20even%20when%20they%20want%20to%20have%20inroads%20among%20Adivasis%20and%20Dalits.%20The%20OBC%20is%20a%20community%2C%20especially%20the%20dominant%20OBCs%2C%20that%20the%20RSS%20has%20simply%20not%20been%20able%20to%20cultivate%20in%20that%20sense%2C%20so%20the%20BJP%20would%20not%20want%20this%20to%20grow%20further%20and%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20quite%20know%20what%20stand%20to%20take%2C%20and%20hence%20their%20desire%20to%20wriggle%20out%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fwatch-mediabol-urmilesh-three-decades-mandal-kamandal-media%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%20%7C%20Three%20Decades%20of%20Mandal%2C%20Kamandal%20and%20Media%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20are%20saying%20that%20if%20this%20becomes%20a%20cascading%20effect%20across%20states%2C%20then%20it%20will%20become%20difficult%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20look%20away%20from%20it%2C%20and%20it%20could%20become%20a%20major%20talking%20point%20going%20into%20the%20elections%20next%20year.%20But%20I%20also%20want%20to%20speak%20to%20you%20about%20the%20larger%20political%20implications%20of%20this%20%5Bissue%5D%2C%20since%20we%20are%20talking%20about%20elections.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20demand%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20is%20not%20only%20gaining%20ground%20through%20different%20states%2C%20but%20even%20among%20the%20allies%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fbihar-caste-survey-sp-bsp-congress-apna-dal-press-for-similar-exercise-in-up%2Farticle67375465.ece%5C%22%3EApna%20Dal%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finterview-fully-assured-caste-census-demands-will-be-met-by-bjp-o-p-rajbhar%5C%22%3EOm%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20even%20its%20allies%20in%20Bihar.%20They%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fcaste-census-sanjay-nishad-interview-bihar-survey-8972570%2F%5C%22%3ESanjay%20Nishad%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E.%20All%20these%20BJP%20allies%20have%20spoken%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20caste%20census.%20Do%20you%20see%20this%20political%20moment%2C%20with%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20data%2C%20becoming%20a%20Mandal%C2%A0%202.0%20moment%20of%20sorts%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20precisely%20what%20the%20BJP%20is%20worried%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBihar%20is%20not%20just%20Bihar.%20Bihar%20has%20an%20immediate%20impact%20on%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20As%20you%20mentioned%2C%20all%20these%20allies%20of%20the%20BJP%20represent%20the%20EBCs.%20They%20represent%20smaller%20OBC%20communities%20which%20have%20a%20very%20strong%20presence.%20So%2C%20these%20demands%20are%20likely%20to%20come%20up.%20This%20is%20why%20the%20BJP%20is%20concerned%2C%20because%20there%20is%20no%20way%20it%20can%20frontally%20say%20no%20to%20them.%20This%20is%20really%20the%20political%20electoral%20dilemma%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20facing.%20This%20would%20happen%20in%20state%20after%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Maharashtra%2C%20too%2C%20it%20would%20be%20impossible%20for%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20to%20say%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20a%20caste%20census.%20So%2C%20there%20would%20be%20pressure%20from%20its%20allies%2C%20from%20within%20the%20BJP%2C%20as%20was%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Bihar%2C%20but%20increasingly%2C%20in%20other%20states%20as%20well%2C%20because%20the%20BJP%20has%20expanded%2C%20and%20in%20many%20states%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20in%20power%2C%20because%20of%20support%20from%20the%20lower%20section%20of%20the%20OBCs%2C%20there%20would%20be%20demand%20from%20within%20the%20BJP%20to%20support%20the%20caste%20census.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20would%20become%20difficult.%20I%20would%20underline%20the%20fact%20that%20when%20we%20speak%20of%20a%20caste%20census%2C%20we%20only%20think%20of%20OBCs%2C%20and%20when%20we%20think%20of%20OBCs%2C%20we%20think%20only%20of%20the%20upper%20crust%20of%20the%20OBCs%20%E2%80%93%20Yadavs%2C%20Kurmis%2C%20Kunbis%2C%20Gowdas%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20But%20the%20real%20advantage%20of%20this%20survey%20is%20that%20it%20puts%20the%20focus%20on%20the%20lower%20end%2C%20the%20extremely%20backward%20%5Bcastes%2Fclasses%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20very%20large%20number%20of%20communities.%20Each%20one%20of%20them%20is%20numerically%20very%20small.%20But%20%5Bif%5D%20put%20together%2C%20they%20constitute%20a%20very%20big%20chunk.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20not%20benefitted%20from%20the%20OBC%20reservations%2C%20and%20the%20same%20applies%20to%20Muslims.%20There%20is%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20Pasmanda%20backward%20Muslims.%20The%20real%20advantage%20of%20this%20survey%2C%20both%20in%20terms%20of%20policy%20and%20politics%2C%20will%20be%20a%20greater%20focus%20and%20attention%20on%20these%20sections%20which%20have%20historically%20been%20neglected%2C%20and%20this%20could%20be%20their%20moment%20in%20the%20sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESravasti%20Dasgupta%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EAll%20right%20let%E2%80%99s%20leave%20it%20to%20that%20Mr.%20Yadav.%20Thank%20you%20so%20much%20for%20joining%20us%20at%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EYogendra%20Yadav%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EThank%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696948212000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F10170711%2FScreenshot-2023-10-06-at-10.47.08-AM_cleanup-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3