2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ESurya%20Pulagam%20was%20deeply%20moved%20by%20farmer%20suicides%20and%20wanted%20to%20prevent%20it%20and%20address%20the%20issues%20faced%20by%20farmers.%20To%20do%20so%2C%20he%20founded%20Praan%20Wellness%20in%202018%20with%20Swetha%20Dutt%20in%20Hyderabad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20mental%20health%20foundation%20was%20originally%20focused%20on%20suicide%20prevention%20among%20farmers%20and%20rural%20children%20and%20has%20extended%20to%20urban%20communites%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20need%20for%20building%20a%20community%20around%20mental%20health%20and%20wellbeing%20that%20provides%20a%20comprehensive%20support%20system%20and%20safe%20space%20along%20with%20a%20means%20to%20address%20and%20manage%20mental%20health%20issues.%20We%20should%20contribute%20to%20a%20society%20where%20seeking%20assistance%20is%20not%20just%20accepted%20but%20encouraged%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Surya.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20offer%20guidance%20and%20counselling%2C%20both%20online%20and%20offline%20starting%20at%20Rs%20450.%20They%20also%20run%20a%20Volunteer%20Initiative%20Program%20(VIP)%20which%20helps%20in%20spreading%20awareness%20and%20Employee%20Assistance%20Program%20(EAP)%20for%20work-related%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Foundation%20also%20provides%20a%20distress%20call%20helpline%208142800800%20which%20helps%20individuals%20and%20runs%2024*7.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20contact%20them%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpraanwellness.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Col%20start%3D%5C%223%5C%22%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESoulUp%3A%20Peer%20Conversations%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2Fsoulup-1681908924.jpg