ate%20didn't%20seem%20beyond%20the%20realms%20of%20possibility%20-%20a%20longstanding%20sticking%20point%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%20%26quot%3BGood%20negotiations%26quot%3B%20are%20ongoing%20to%20achieve%20that%20goal%2C%20the%2038-year-old%20de%20facto%20Saudi%20leader%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Fox%20News%20last%20month.%20The%20US%20is%20pushing%20the%20talks%20and%20%26quot%3Bthe%20biggest%20historical%20deal%20since%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Cold%20war%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20realistic%20prospect%2C%20he%20told%20the%20TV%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20last%20weekend's%20deadly%20attacks%20by%20Hamas%20on%20Israel%2C%20those%20hopes%20have%20been%20upended.%20The%20incursion%20also%20turns%20attention%20toward%20Iran%2C%20which%20has%20never%20wavered%20from%20its%20policy%20of%20armed%20resistance%20to%20Israel%20and%20is%20a%20financial%20and%20military%20backer%20to%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20Crown%20Prince%20Mohammed%20appears%20to%20be%20already%20tempering%20his%20enthusiasm%20for%20a%20deal%20with%20Israel%20in%20the%20short-term%20by%20defaulting%20to%20the%20kingdom's%20more%20solemn%20official%20stance%20on%20the%20Israeli-Palestinian%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20kingdom%20will%20continue%20to%20stand%20by%20the%20Palestinian%20nation%20in%20its%20quest%20for%20its%20legitimate%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release%20after%20a%20phone%20conversation%20with%20Palestinian%20Authority%20President%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESanam%20Vakil%2C%20director%20of%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20North%20Africa%20program%20at%20London's%20Chatham%20House%20think%20tank%2C%20said%20the%20attack%20underscored%20the%20idea%20that%20a%20policy%20of%20%26quot%3Bcontainment%26quot%3B%20on%20Iran%20and%20the%20Palestinian-Israeli%20conflict%20isn't%20an%20effective%20way%20of%20managing%20regional%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20pours%20cold%20water%20on%20the%20mirage%20of%20de-escalation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMinimizing%20Threats%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMBS%2C%20as%20the%20oil-rich%20kingdom's%20crown%20prince%20is%20known%2C%20had%20previously%20taken%20steps%20to%20deescalate%20regional%20tensions%20and%20minimize%20threats%20to%20his%20multi-trillion-dollar%20plan%20to%20transform%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20economy%20by%202030.%20The%20kingdom%20is%20the%20home%20of%20Islam's%20two%20most%20holiest%20sites%2C%20giving%20it%20particular%20importance%20in%20the%20region%20and%20creating%20a%20tricky%20balancing%20act%20between%20religious%20and%20secular%20objectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20prince's%20pitch%20has%20been%20that%20economic%20development%20and%20prosperity%20in%20his%20country%20will%20benefit%20a%20region%20mired%20for%20too%20long%20in%20wars%20and%20ideological%20differences.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20that%20end%2C%20he%20forged%20a%20Chinese-brokered%20deal%20in%20March%20with%20regional%20rival%20Iran%2C%20embarked%20on%20direct%20negotiations%20with%20Tehran%20-%20backed%20Houthi%20rebels%20in%20neighbouring%20Yemen%20-%20against%20whom%20he%20had%20waged%20war%20for%20eight%20years%20-%20and%20made%20overtures%20to%20Syria's%20pariah%20President%20Bashar%20Al-Assad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20said%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20own%20economic%20success%20hinged%20on%20a%20stable%2C%20peaceful%20and%20thriving%20region%20that%20gave%20everyone%20including%20Iranians%20and%20Palestinians%20%26quot%3Ba%20good%20life.%26quot%3B%20He%20told%20Fox%20News%20he%20wanted%20something%20substantive%20for%20the%20Palestinians%20as%20part%20of%20a%20three-way%20bargain%20with%20Israel%20and%20the%20US%2C%20but%20declined%20to%20be%20specific.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeadly%20Fallout%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas's%20surprise%20attack%20on%20Israel%20-%20which%20has%20left%20at%20least%201%2C600%20people%20dead%20on%20both%20sides%20-%20effectively%20rules%20out%2