ot%3BWe%20play%20better%20spinners%20in%20the%20net%20sessions.%20Like%20if%20you%20see%20Rashid%2C%20Nabi%2C%20Noor%20and%20Mujeeb%2C%20we%20play%20them%20every%20day.%20So%2C%20I%20think%20our%20team%20is%20far%20better%20in%20playing%20spin%20bowling.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20that%20game%20you%20know%20we%20struggled%20but%20you%20can't%20say%20that%20you%20are%20not%20good%20enough%20on%20one%20game.%20So%20that%20game%20is%20gone%20now%20and%20we%20know%20we%20can%20play%20spinners%20better%20and%20we%20will%20try%20to%20come%20back%20in%20next%20game%20in%20every%20department%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shahidi%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20team's%20trump%20card%20Rashid%20Khan%20went%20wicket%20less%20against%20Bangladesh%20as%20opposition%20batters%20chose%20to%20play%20safe%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENot%20taking%20too%20much%20risks%20against%20Rashid%20has%20been%20a%20trend%20but%20Shahidi%20said%20they%20are%20not%20too%20bothered%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSee%2C%20Rashid%20is%20the%20best%20bowler%20in%20ODI%20and%20T20s%2C%20so%20whatever%20opposition%20is%20doing%2C%20we%20don't%20care%20about%20that%2C%20like%20how%20they%20play%2C%20they%20want%20to%20play%20Rashid%2C%20but%20for%20us%20the%20important%20thing%20is%20how%20he%20has%20planned%20against%20the%20opposition.%20So%20that%20matters%20for%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20playing%20ODIs%20over%20the%20last%20six%20months%20so%20he%20knows%20how%20to%20bowl%20and%20he%20knows%20how%20to%20bowl%20to%20every%20team.%20He%20has%20the%20quality%20and%20whenever%20it's%20his%20day%20he%20can%20do%20anything%20against%20the%20opposition%2C%20so%20we%20are%20expecting%20and%20we%20are%20hopeful%20that%20he%20delivers%20in%20tomorrow's%20game.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20used%20to%20be%20home%20base%20for%20Afghanistan%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20Their%20stars%20players%20are%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20I