r-jobs%20scam%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20October%205.%20On%20the%20very%20same%20day%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20arrested%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fenforcement-directorate-conducts-searches-at-aap-mp-sanjay-singhs-house%5C%22%3ESanjay%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case.%20Soon%20after%20he%20was%20granted%20bail%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20Tejashwi%20appeared%20before%20the%20media%20to%20condemn%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20rather%20than%20speak%20effusively%20about%20the%20bail%20and%20his%20%E2%80%98uprightness%E2%80%99%20makes%20him%20stand%20tall%20among%20the%20current%20crop%20of%20politicians%20for%20whom%20politics%20is%20all%20about%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20is%20torturing%20all%20regional%20parties%20which%20are%20doing%20good%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20extending%20solidarity%20to%20AAP%2C%20which%20is%20in%20crisis%20as%20three%20of%20its%20top%20leaders%20are%20currently%20imprisoned.%20%E2%80%9CI%20condemn%20the%20arrest%20of%20Sanjay%20Singh.%20The%20BJP%20is%20harassing%20the%20parties%20which%20are%20addressing%20the%20issues%20concerning%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-rise-of-tejashwi-yadav-signals-significant-change-in-bihar-politics%5C%22%3EThe%20Rise%20of%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20Signals%20Significant%20Change%20in%20Bihar%20Politics%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20is%20frightened%20more%20at%20the%20release%20of%20the%20caste%20survey%20report%20in%20Bihar%20and%20Bihar%20government%20giving%20employment%20in%20lakhs%20to%20the%20youths.%20They%20(the%20BJP)%20are%20incapable%20of%20fighting%20a%20political%20battle.%20The%20only%20recourse%20they%20know%20is%20to%20misuse%20the%20central%20agencies%20against%20its%20opponents.%20But%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20fear.%20These%20diabolical%20moves%20will%20strengthen%20our%20resolve%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20up%20on%20Tejashwi%E2%80%99s%20statements%2C%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20MP%20and%20spokesperson%20Manoj%20Jha%20personally%20visited%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20family%20to%20extend%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20support.%20Although%20other%20constituent%20parties%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20condemned%20the%20arrest%20of%20Singh%2C%20it%20was%20only%20the%20RJD%20which%20went%20a%20step%20further%20to%20send%20its%20representative%20to%20his%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3ERJD-AAP%20relationship%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETejashwi%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20onslaught%20on%20AAP%20is%20sharply%20at%20variance%20with%20the%20cold%20relationship%20that%20his%20father%20and%20RJD%20chief%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20are%20known%20to%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELalu%20Yadav%20has%20been%20critical%20of%20AAP%20since%20the%20period%20it%20emerged%20from%20the%20Anna%20Hazare-led%20movement%20against%20corruption%20in%202014.%20Lalu%20has%20differences%20with%20Kejriwal%20and%20AAP%20for%20he%20perceives%20them%20as%20%E2%80%9Canti-Mandal%E2%80%9D%20and%20inimical%20to%20the%20battle%20for%20social%20justice.%20He%20also%20suspects%20that%20Kejriwal%20is%20closer%20to%20the%20Sangh%3Cem%3E%20parivar%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20philosophy%20which%20the%20former%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20detests.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKejriwal%20and%20most%20of%20his%20party%20men%2C%20including%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20were%20very%20critical%20of%20Lalu%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20corruption.%20They%20perceived%20that%20their%20association%20with%20the%20RJD%20in%20any%20manner%20would%20cost%20their%20credentials%20as%20%E2%80%98anti-corruption%E2%80%99%20crusaders%20%E2%80%93%20the%20plank%20on%20which%20it%20emerged%20on%20the%20political%20map.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20when%20Lalu%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Findia-news-india%2Fwhy-the-lalu-kejriwal-hug-became-a-controversy%2F%5C%22%3Ehugged%3C%2Fa%3E%20Kejriwal%20at%20a%20meeting%20(of%20Mahagathbandhan)%2C%20Kejriwal%20said%20openly%20that%20he%20did%20not%20like%20it.%20Lalu%20then%20responded%20by%20saying%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccourtesy%20of%20%5Ba%5D%20public%20stage%E2%80%9D%20while%20clarifying%20that%20there%20was%20no%20change%20of%20heart%20on%20his%20part%20in%20the%20way%20he%20viewed%20AAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09170730%2FThe-Wire-36.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09170730%2FThe-Wire-36.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09170730%2FThe-Wire-36-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09170730%2FThe-Wire-36-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679120%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ELalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%20Photos%3A%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20(Government%20of%20India%2FGODL%20License)%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20(Government%20of%20the%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%2FGODL%20License)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20Tejashwi%E2%80%99s%20approach%20to%20Kejriwal%20and%20AAP%20is%20in%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20that%20of%20his%20father.%20It%20goes%20without%20saying%20that%20Kejriwal%20will%20rethink%20his%20and%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20relationship%20with%20the%20RJD%2C%20particularly%20after%20Tejashwi%E2%80%99s%20public%20show%20of%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20appears%20to%20have%20brought%20the%20RJD%20and%20AAP%20closer%20are%20the%20central%20investigating%20agencies%20%E2%80%93%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20and%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20%E2%80%93%20framing%20their%20leaders%20in%20corruption%20cases.%20Both%20parties%20say%20the%20cases%20represent%20a%20misuse%20of%20central%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20one%20day%20after%20the%20Rouse%20Avenue%20court%20granted%20bail%20to%20Tejashwi%20and%20the%20CBI%20arrested%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20questioned%20the%20CBI%20and%20ED%E2%80%99s%20charges%20against%20another%20AAP%20leader%20and%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20of%20Delhi%20Manish%20Sisodia%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fno-money-has-come-to-manish-sisodia-how-will-you-bring-him-under-pmla-sc-to-ed%5C%22%3Estrong%20words%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWhere%20is%20the%20proof%3F%20Where%20is%20the%20evidence%3F%20Except%20for%20the%20statement%20of%20Dinesh%20Arora%20(a%20businessman)%2C%20is%20there%20any%20other%20evidence%3F%20How%20will%20you%20bring%20Manish%20Sisodia%20under%20the%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%3F%E2%80%9D%20the%20top%20court%20said%20whilst%20hearing%20Sisodia%E2%80%99s%20bail%20plea.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20observation%20has%20created%20doubts%20about%20actions%20against%20the%20AAP%20leaders%2C%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20two%20central%20agencies%20have%20implicated%20Tejashwi%20in%20the%20land-for-job%20case%20is%20hardly%20convincing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20CBI%20and%20ED%2C%20some%20candidates%20obtained%20jobs%20in%20the%20railways%20in%20lieu%20of%20plots%20of%20land%20that%20they%20gave%20to%20Lalu%20when%20the%20latter%20was%20the%20minister%20for%20railways%20(2004-09).%20Tejashwi%20was%20a%20minor%20at%20that%20time%2C%20playing%20cricket%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Board%20of%20Cricket%20Control%20of%20India%20(BCCI)%E2%80%99s%20Under-15%20team%20and%20living%20away%20from%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20CBI%20itself%20dropped%20these%20allegations%20in%202011%20after%20it%20had%20said%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Cno%20evidence%E2%80%9D%20to%20carry%20them%20forward.%20But%20the%20CBI%20and%20ED%20suddenly%20raided%20establishments%20connected%20to%20Lalu%20in%20Patna%20and%20Delhi%20in%202017%2C%20when%20Tejashwi%20was%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20in%20the%20Nitish%20Kumar-led%20first%20Mahagathbandhan%20government%2C%20reopening%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcbi-tejashwi-yadav-lalu-prasad-nitish-bjp-jdu-rjd-irctc%5C%22%3ESo%20Why%20Is%20the%20CBI%20After%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20Now%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20fell%20silent%20again%20for%20five%20years%20after%20Nitish%20broke%20away%20from%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20and%20rejoined%20the%20BJP.%20However%2C%20they%20carried%20out%20raids%20on%20Lalu%20and%20his%20family%20members%20after%20Nitish%20returned%20to%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20again%20in%20August%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIntriguingly%2C%20Tejashwi%20didn%E2%80%99t%20figure%20in%20the%20original%20chargesheet%20of%20the%20land-for-jobs%20scam%20case.%20But%20the%20CBI%20named%20him%20in%20the%20supplementary%20chargesheet%20filed%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETejashwi%E2%80%99s%20attributes%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETejashwi%20Yadav%20broadly%20appears%20to%20have%20three%20special%20attributes%20that%20contrast%20him%20with%20other%20young%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20his%20complete%20focus%20on%20the%20issues%20concerning%20the%20people.%20For%20example%2C%20during%20the%202020%20assembly%20elections%2C%20when%20he%20was%20fighting%20a%20lonely%20battle%20against%20the%20BJP-Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20with%20his%20father%20in%20jail%2C%20Tejashwi%20promised%2010%2C00%2C000%20jobs%20to%20the%20youth%20if%20his%20party%20was%20elected%20to%20power.%20He%20based%20his%20campaign%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20employment%20and%20outsmarted%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20%E2%80%93%20who%20addressed%20as%20many%20as%2031%20election%20rallies%20in%20Bihar%20at%20that%20time.%20Even%20though%20the%20RJD%20was%20unable%20to%20form%20the%20government%2C%20it%20emerged%20as%20the%20single%20largest%20party%20with%2078%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2F596103-lalu-tejaswi-pti.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20Tejashwi%20Yadav.%20Credit%3A%20PTI%2FFiles%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-175013%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22360%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ELalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20Tejashwi%20Yadav.%20Credit%3A%20PTI%2FFiles%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20as%20deputy%20CM%2C%20he%20has%20shown%20that%20he%20can%20implement%20what%20he%20promised.%20The%20Nitish%20Kumar%20government%20has%20already%20given%20over%20two%20lakh%20jobs%20since%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20government%20was%20formed%20in%20August%20last%20year.%20Bihar%20is%20said%20to%20be%20far%20ahead%20of%20others%20in%20providing%20employment%20to%20the%20youth%2C%20whereas%20Modi%20and%20his%20Union%20government%20have%20failed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESecondly%2C%20he%20had%20joined%20hands%20with%20Nitish%20Kumar%20to%20ask%20for%20the%20caste-based%20census%20when%20he%20was%20in%20the%20opposition.%20Now%2C%20Bihar%20is%20the%20first%20state%20to%20have%20come%20out%20with%20the%20caste%20survey%20report%2C%20giving%20strength%20to%20INDIA%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20against%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20way%2C%20the%20young%20Tejashwi%20is%20quite%20sharp%20in%20identifying%20the%20issues%20that%20would%20succeed%20against%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20gargantuan%20election%20machine.%20Secondly%2C%20he%20is%20bold%2C%20a%20trait%20that%20he%20has%20inherited%20from%20his%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20personally%20went%20to%20express%20support%20to%20West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20during%20the%202021%20assembly%20elections%2C%20when%20Modi%20had%20mocked%20Mamata%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EDidi-o-Didi%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20investigating%20agencies%20were%20after%20her%20party%E2%80%99s%20top%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMamata%20was%20overwhelmed%20by%20his%20support%20at%20the%20time%20when%20political%20leaders%20from%20other%20parties%20acted%20diplomatically%20to%20avoid%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98wrath%E2%80%99.%20As%20a%20railway%20minister%2C%20she%20had%20tabled%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Fmagazine%2Ffocus%2Fstory%2Flalu-vs-mamata-whos-right-17676-2010-01-11%5C%22%3EWhite%20Paper%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20Lalu%E2%80%99s%20tenure.%20But%20when%20she%20came%20to%20attend%20the%20first%20conclave%20of%20the%20opposition%20parties%20in%20August%2C%20she%20bowed%20down%20before%20Lalu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20Tejashwi%E2%80%99s%20third%20but%20equally%20important%20attribute%20is%20deference%20to%20elders.%20He%20has%20the%20utmost%20respect%20for%20Nitish%2C%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20contemporary%2C%20and%20avoids%20speaking%20when%20he%20is%20with%20the%20chief%20minister.%20He%20touches%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20feet%20whenever%20he%20goes%20out%20of%20home%20and%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENalin%20Verma%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20media%20educator%2C%20and%20independent%20researcher%20in%20folklore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696943735000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F24105952%2F2022_8img22_Aug_2022_PTI08_22_2022_000199B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftejashwi-yadav-stands-apart-today-young-politicians%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20deput