3Cp%3EThe%20distance%20from%20her%20hotel%20to%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20was%20barely%202%20km%2C%20the%20actor%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20seemed%20impossible%20with%20%26quot%3Bdreadful%20sounds%20of%20explosions%20at%20very%20close%20range%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20open%20fire%20on%20vehicles%20on%20the%20roads%20and%20the%20situation%20out%20on%20the%20streets%20was%20'extremely%20dangerous'.%20Just%20then%2C%20we%20heard%20a%20second%20siren%20go%20off%20and%20were%20rushed%20back%20down%20into%20the%20basement%20shelter%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued%2C%20adding%20that%20their%20phone%20batteries%20were%20fast%20running%20out%20and%20they%20were%20beginning%20to%20lose%20cell%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2038-year-old%20actor%2C%20who%20was%20in%20Haifa%20for%20the%20screening%20of%20her%20film%20'Akelli'%2C%20said%20help%20came%20in%20from%20completely%20unexpected%20quarters%3A%20calls%20from%20her%20Israeli%20co-actors%2C%20Indian%20and%20Israeli%20embassies%20and%20a%20taxi%20driver.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20journey%20out%20of%20our%20Tel%20Aviv%20hotel%20was%20not%20easy%2C%20to%20put%20it%20mildly...%20praying%20the%20whole%20time%2C%20even%20crying%20sometimes%2C%20we%20held%20onto%20each%20other%20for%20courage%20to%20keep%20on%20going%2C%20somehow%20making%20it%20to%20Ben%20Gurion%20Airport.%20The%20wait%20between%20one%20formality%20to%20the%20next%20for%20boarding%20a%20flight%20has%20never%20been%20more%20excruciating%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20count%20in%20Israel%20has%20surged%20above%20900%20from%20the%20worst%20attack%20in%20the%20country's%2075-year%20history%2C%20while%20Gaza%20officials%20have%20reported%20687%20people%20killed%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20someone%20who%20has%20barely%20escaped%20a%20war%20zone%2C%20I%20cannot%20be%20more%20grateful%20today...I'm%20back%20home%20and%20safe%20with%20my%20family%20and%20my%20loved%20ones.%20But%20with%20an%20experience%20that%20has%20made%20me%20immensely%20grateful%20for%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20that%20we%20almost%20take%20for%20granted.%20I%20am%20ever%20so%20grateful%20to%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20and%20the%20Israeli%20Embassy%2C%20for%20their%20help%20and%20guidance%20in%20bringing%20my%20team%20and%20me%20back%20safe%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696943520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F012snd4c_nushrratt-bharuccha-1200_625x300_10_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnushrratt-bharuccha-israel-woke-up-to-sounds-of-bombs-going-off-says-bollywood-actor-on-israel-horror-4468239%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Having%20celebrated%20her%20film's%20selection%20at%20the%20Haifa%20Film%20Festival%20the%20previous%20evening%2C%20she%20woke%20up%20the%20next%20day%20to%20%26quot%3Bdeafening%20sounds%20of%20bombs%20going%20off%26quot%3B%2C%20recounted%20Bollywood%20actor%20Nushrratt%20Bharuccha%2C%20who%20was%20briefly%20stuck%20in%20Tel%20Aviv.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnushrratt-bharuccha-israel-woke-up-to-sounds-of-bombs-going-off-says-bollywood-actor-on-israel-horror-4468239%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnushrratt-bharuccha-israel-woke-up-to-sounds-of-bombs-going-off-says-bollywood-actor-on-israel-horror-4468239%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnushrratt-bharuccha-israel-woke-up-to-sounds-of-bombs-going-off-says-bollywood-actor-on-israel-horror-4468239%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prakash%20Chhabria-led%20Orbit%20moves%20SC%20over%20Finolex%20Cables%20non-disclosure%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696943281000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_m