sations%20raised%20objection%20over%20four%20of%20the%20many%20speakers%20who%20were%20invited%20to%20the%20festival.%20The%20objection%20was%20against%20inviting%20journalists%20and%20authors%20like%20Aakar%20Patel%2C%20Josy%20Joseph%2C%20Shruti%20Ganpataye%20and%20Shivam%20Shankar%20Singh%20to%20the%20festival.%20For%20the%20February%202024%20edition%2C%20around%2040%20speakers%20were%20invited.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPatel%2C%20a%20vocal%20critic%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20recently%20came%20out%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.in%2FAakar-Patel%2Fe%2FB075J9J5TN%2Fref%3Ddp_byline_cont_book_1%5C%22%3Ebooks%20that%20focus%20on%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20BJP%20government%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Investigative%20journalist%20and%20author%20Joseph%E2%80%99s%20book%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Silent%20Coup%3A%20A%20History%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Deep%20State%3C%2Fem%3E%20closely%20looks%20at%20bias%20that%20runs%20deep%20in%20the%20Indian%20security%20establishment%20against%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20Ganpatye%2C%20a%20Mumbai-based%20journalist%2C%20recently%20came%20out%20with%20her%20debut%20book%20%3Cem%3EWho%20Will%20Bell%20The%20Cow%3F%3A%20Beef%20Ban%3A%20Decoding%20its%20cultural%2C%20social%2C%20and%20economical%20aspects%20in%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EHow%20to%20Win%20an%20Indian%20Election%3A%20What%20Political%20Parties%20Don%E2%80%99t%20Want%20You%20to%20Know%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0book%20looks%20at%20political%20campaigns%20and%20disinformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20how%20my%20book%20%E2%80%9CWho%20Will%20Bell%20The%20Cow%3F%E2%80%9D%20was%20withdrawn%20for%20Vidarbha%20Lit%20Fest.%20I%20appreciate%20the%20honesty%20of%20the%20organisers%20to%20admit%20the%20pressure%20and%20come%20out%20open%20about%20it.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F6vkW9mnaR8%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F6vkW9mnaR8%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C