acksliding%20across%20South%20Asia%2C%20a%20statement%20by%20three%20dozen%20academics%2C%20activists%20and%20concerned%20individuals%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20raids%20and%20arrests%2C%20the%20statement%20says%2C%20are%20part%20of%20a%20growing%20trend%20in%20India%20to%20harass%20and%20intimidate%20independent%20media%20by%20the%20misuse%20of%20the%20police%20and%20state%20agencies%20for%20narrow%20political%20gains.%20They%20pointed%20to%20similar%20incidents%20in%20Bangladesh%20and%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20latest%20developments%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20India%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20ring%20an%20alarm%20bell%20for%20all%20of%20us%20in%20South%20Asia%20who%20care%20about%20preserving%20our%20democratic%20rights%20and%20freedoms.%20In%20their%20decided%20attempts%20to%20target%20journalists%2C%20or%20to%20harass%20or%20silence%20other%20dissenting%20voices%2C%20our%20governments%20have%20begun%20to%20employ%20the%20new%20tactic%20of%20portraying%20journalists%20and%20citizen-activists%20who%20dare%20to%20expose%20the%20misdeeds%20of%20those%20in%20power%20as%20%E2%80%98anti-national%E2%80%99%20and%20threats%20to%20national%20security%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDenying%20citizens%20the%20democratic%20space%20for%20critical%20questioning%20will%20drag%20South%20Asian%20countries%20into%20a%20new%20phase%20of%20authoritarian%20decay%2C%20said%20the%20signatories%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20are%20Sri%20Lankan.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTherefore%2C%20struggles%20for%20media%20freedom%20in%20India%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20or%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20region%20is%20to%20be%20viewed%20as%20integral%20to%20the%20struggle%20for%20democracy%20in%20South%20Asia%20as%20a%20whole.%20Amid%20the%20heightening%20attacks%20on%20free%20media%20and%20the%20right%20to%20free%20expression%2C%20we%20must%20respond%20collectively%20as%20South%20Asians.%C2%A0%20We%20must%20resist%20tyranny%20in%20all%20forms%2C%20and%20fight%20to%20restore%20and%20strengthen%20our%20fundamental%20rights%20and%20democratic%20freedoms.%20We%20must%20resolve%20to%20look%20out%20for%20each%20other%2C%20assert%20our%20rights%2C%20and%20defend%20our%20freedoms%20within%20and%20beyond%20our%20individual%20nation-states%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20statement%2C%20and%20the%20list%20of%20signatories%2C%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECondemning%20the%20heightening%20attack%20on%20free%20expression%20and%20democratic%20rights%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20imposition%20of%20severe%20restrictions%20on%20the%20independent%20media%20and%20media%20professionals%20by%20governments%20has%20become%20a%20recurring%20feature%20of%20the%20continuing%20crisis%20of%20democracy%20in%20South%20Asia.%20The%20unending%20assault%20on%20free%20expression%20and%20democratic%20rights%20in%20South%20Asia%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20country-specific%20development.%20Neither%20is%20it%20confined%20to%20specific%20nation%20states.%20Rather%20it%20is%20a%20regional%20phenomenon%2C%20signalling%20a%20new%20and%20worsening%20phase%20of%20democratic%20backsliding%20in%20South%20Asia.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20recent%20raids%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20on%2046%20houses%20of%20journalists%20connected%20with%20the%20Indian%20news%20portal%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20illustrates%20this%20shocking%20trend.%20More%20unsettling%20is%20the%20arrest%20of%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%2C%20its%20Editor-in-Chief%2C%20and%20Amith%20Chakravorty%2C%20its%20Head%20of%20Human%20Resources%2C%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20investigating%20them%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Cterror%20case%20with%20Chinese%20links%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Indian%20media%20has%20reported%20that%20the%20police%20has%20blatantly%20disregarded%20the%20legally%20sanctioned%20procedures%20in%20arresting%20the%20senior%20journalist%20and%20his%20colleague.%C2%A0%20The%20authorities%20are%20yet%20to%20make%20known%20any%20material%20on%20the%20website%20with%20links%20to%20any%20%E2%80%9Cterrorist%20activity%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9CChinese%20propaganda%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20join%20the%20progressive%20media%2C%20civil%20society%20organisations%20and%20activists%20in%20India%20to%20condemn%20in%20no%20uncertain%20terms%20this%20brazen%20attack%20by%20the%20government%20on%20the%20free%20media.%20Harassment%20and%20intimidation%20of%20the%20independent%20media%20by%20the%20misuse%20of%20the%20police%20and%20state%20agencies%20for%20narrow%20political%20gains%20is%20part%20of%20a%20growing%20trend%20in%20a%20country%20claimed%20to%20be%20the%20%E2%80%98Mother%20of%20Democracy.%E2%80%99%20Many%20commentators%20have%20likened%20this%20trend%20to%20the%20stifling%20times%20of%20the%20Emergency%20in%20India%20during%20the%201970s%2C%20although%20a%20State%20of%20Emergency%20has%20not%20been%20formally%20declared%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20recent%20weeks%2C%20journalists%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20too%2C%20have%20been%20subjected%20to%20enormous%20pressure%2C%20by%20way%20of%20judicial%20harassment%2C%20police%20violence%2C%20online%20harassment%2C%20attacks%20at%20reporting%20assignments%2C%20and%20intimidation%20of%20journalists%E2%80%99%20families.%20We%20particularly%20take%20note%20of%20the%20recent%20jailing%20of%20Adilur%20Rahman%20Khan%20and%20Nasiruddin%20Elan%2C%20two%20leading%20human%20rights%20campaigners%20attached%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EOdhikar%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Bangladesh%2C%20a%20leading%20human%20rights%20documentation%20and%20reporting%20centre.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20charge%20against%20them%20is%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Epublishing%20and%20circ