0Finance%20Corporation%20(IRFC)%20which%20also%20included%20Shelley%20Verma%2C%20the%20director%20(finance)%20of%20the%20public%20sector%20unit%20(PSU)%20who%20has%20been%20under%20the%20shadow%20of%20a%20controversy%2C%20has%20decided%20to%20adopt%20%E2%80%9Can%20alternate%20method%20of%20selection%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%207%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcorruption-shadow-over-candidate-shortlisted-for-top-job-in-railway-finance-psu%5C%22%3Epublished%20a%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20pointing%20out%20the%20controversy%20surrounding%20Verma%20in%20relation%20to%20a%20corruption%20case%20which%20is%20being%20probed%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI).%20Citing%20the%20case%2C%20this%20correspondent%20had%20mailed%20a%20questionnaire%20to%20railway%20minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%2C%20chairman%20and%20chief%20executive%20officer%20of%20the%20Railway%20Board%20Jaya%20Verma%20Sinha%2C%20Anjali%20Goel%2C%20member%20(finance)%20at%20the%20Railway%20Board%20and%20Shobhana%20Bandopadhyay%2C%20principal%20executive%20director%20(vigilance)%20at%20the%20Railway%20Board%2C%20asking%20why%20an%20official%20under%20the%20scanner%20for%20alleged%20financial%20embezzlement%20has%20been%20shortlisted%20for%20the%20top%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20questionnaire%20also%20asked%20why%20the%20Railway%20Vigilance%20Directorate%20%E2%80%93%20after%20it%20found%20alleged%20financial%20discrepancy%20of%20public%20funds%20in%20which%20Verma%20had%20played%20a%20crucial%20part%20(the%20official%20documents%20were%20perused%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E)%20%E2%80%93%20was%20even%20allowed%20to%20continue%20in%20the%20charge%20of%20CMD%20of%20the%20PSU.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20with%20details%20of%20the%20corruption%20case%20which%20the%20Board%20forwarded%20to%20the%20CBI%20for%20further%20inquiry%20in%20February%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcorruption-shadow-over-candidate-shortlisted-for-top-job-in-railway-finance-psu%5C%22%3Ecan%20be%20read%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%2C%20two%20other%20candidates%20%E2%80%93%20a%20director%20at%20HUDCO%20and%20a%20divisional%20railway%20manager%20with%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20%E2%80%93%20were%20also%20shortlisted%20for%20the%20October%209%20interview%20besides%20Verma.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThough%20neither%20the%20minister%E2%80%99s%20office%20nor%20the%20Railway%20Board%20chief%20and%20Railway%20Vigilance%20principal%20executive%20officer%20replied%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20queries%2C%20the%20Board%20later%20took%20the%20decision%20to%20not%20hire%20either%20Verma%20or%20the%20other%20two%20shortlisted%20candidates.%20As%20per%20the%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20circular%20issued%20later%20on%20October%209%2C%20%E2%80%9CKeeping%20in%20view%20the%20strategic%20importance%20and%20vision%20for%20the%20company%20(IRFC)%20and%20its%20future%2C%20and%20the%20performance%20of%20the%20candidates%20interviewed%2C%20the%20Board%20did%20not%20recommend%20any%20candidate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20circular%20further%20said%2C%20the%20Board%20%E2%80%9Cadvised%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Railways%20to%20choose%20an%20alternate%20method%20of%20selection%2C%20including%20search-cum-selection%20committee%20(SCSC)%2C%20as%20deemed%20appropriate%20for%20the%20selection%2C%20with%20the%20approval%20of%20the%20competent%20authority.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20post%20of%20the%20chairman%20and%20CMD%20of%20IRFC%20has%20been%20lying%20vacant%20for%20a%20year%20now.%20Former%20CMD%20Amitabha%20Banerjee%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-wire-impact-railways-finance-commission-amitabh-banerjee%5C%22%3Edivested%20of%20his%20responsibilities%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9Cwith%20immediate%20effect%E2%80%9D%20after%20